"Menggunakan akun pelanggan untuk e-commerce memungkinkan Anda "
":ref:`mengelola pelanggan <ecommerce/customer_accounts/account-creation>`, "
"mengontrol akses ke :ref:`toko <ecommerce/customer_accounts/shop-access>`, "
":ref:`checkout <ecommerce/customer_accounts/checkout-access>`, atau "
":doc:`portal pelanggan </applications/general/users/user_portals/"
"portal_access>`, dan mendukung :doc:`operasi B2B dan B2C <b2b_b2c>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/customer_accounts.rst:12
msgid ""
"After logging in, customers can access their :doc:`customer portal </"
"applications/general/users/user_portals>` by clicking their username in the "
"top-right corner of the screen and selecting :guilabel:`My Account`. From "
"there, they can view all their documents in one place, such as quotations, "
"orders, invoices, and more."
msgstr ""
