"click :guilabel:`Save`, you are redirected to the product page where you "
"can :ref:`customize it <ecommerce_design/product_page/customization>` using "
"the :doc:`website editor </applications/websites/website/web_design>`. Once "
"you are finished, click :guilabel:`Save`. To configure additional "
"advanced :ref:`product details <ecommerce/products/product-configuration>`, "
"click :guilabel:`Product` in the top-right corner to access the backend "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat produk dari frontend, buka aplikasi Website, klik "
":guilabel:`Baru` :icon:`fa-caret-down` di sudut kanan atas, kemudian pilih "
":guilabel:`Produk`. Masukkan :guilabel:`Nama Produk`, dan detail relevan "
"lainnya seperti :guilabel:`Barcode`, :guilabel:`Harga Penjualan`, default "
":guilabel:`Pajak Penjualan`, dan :ref:`Kategori Website <ecommerce/"
"categories_variants/categories>`, kemudian tambahkan gambar. Setelah Anda "
"mengklik :guilabel:`Simpan`, Anda akan diarahkan ke halaman produk di mana "
"Anda dapat :ref:`menyesuaikannya <ecommerce_design/product_page/"
"customization>` menggunakan :doc:`editor website </applications/websites/"
"website/web_design>`. Setelah selesai, klik :guilabel:`Simpan`. Untuk "
"mengonfigurasi :ref:`detail produk <ecommerce/products/product-configuration>"
"` lanjutan tambahan, klik :guilabel:`Produk` di sudut kanan atas untuk "
"mengakses formulir produk backend."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/configuration/products.rst:32
