":guilabel:`Opsi Pembelian`: (Tidak)aktifkan tombol :ref:`Beli Sekarang "
"<ecommerce/checkout/buy-now>` dan/atau pemilih :guilabel:`Kuantitas`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/ecommerce_design/product_page.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Actions`: Enable the :ref:`wishlist <ecommerce/products/"
"additional_features/wishlists>` and the :ref:`product comparison <ecommerce/"
"products/additional_features/product-comparison>` features."
