#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:48
msgid "Karma points"
msgstr "Poin karma"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:50
msgid ""
"Karma points can be given to users based on different forum interactions. "
"They can be used to determine which forum functionalities users can access, "
"from being able to vote on posts to having moderator rights. They are also "
"used to set user :ref:`ranks <forum/ranks>`."
msgstr ""
"Poin karma dapat diberikan kepada user berdasarkan berbagai interaksi forum. "
"Poin ini dapat digunakan untuk menentukan fungsionalitas forum mana yang "
"dapat diakses user, dari kemampuan memberikan suara pada postingan hingga "
"memiliki hak moderator. Poin karma juga digunakan untuk menetapkan "
":ref:`peringkat <forum/ranks>` user."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:55
msgid ""
"A user's karma points are shared across all forums, courses, etc., of a "
"single Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"Poin karma user dibagikan di semua forum, kursus, dll., dari satu website "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:56
msgid ""
"eLearning users can earn karma points through different :ref:`course "
"interactions <elearning/karma>` and by :ref:`completing quizzes <elearning/"
"content-quiz>`."
msgstr ""
"Pengguna eLearning dapat memperoleh poin karma melalui berbagai "
":ref:`interaksi kursus <elearning/karma>` dan dengan :ref:`menyelesaikan "
"kuis <elearning/content-quiz>`."

