"Rights` tab. Select a value to edit it."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi berapa banyak poin karma yang diperlukan untuk "
"mengakses berbagai fungsionalitas forum, buka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Forums`, pilih forum, dan buka tab :guilabel:`Karma "
"Related Rights`. Pilih nilai untuk mengeditnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:119
msgid ""
"Some functionalities, such as :guilabel:`Edit all posts`, :guilabel:`Close "
"all posts`, :guilabel:`Delete all posts`, :guilabel:`Moderate posts`, "
"and :guilabel:`Unlink all comments`, are rather sensitive. Make sure to "
"understand the consequences of giving *any* user reaching the set karma "
"requirements access to such functionalities."
msgstr ""
"Beberapa fungsionalitas, seperti :guilabel:`Edit all posts`, "
":guilabel:`Close all posts`, :guilabel:`Delete all posts`, "
":guilabel:`Moderate posts`, dan :guilabel:`Unlink all comments`, cukup "
"sensitif. Pastikan untuk memahami konsekuensi memberikan akses ke "
"fungsionalitas tersebut kepada *semua* user yang mencapai persyaratan karma "
"yang ditetapkan."

