"under :guilabel:`Authorized Users`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`A selected list of users`: user yang dipilih di bawah "
":guilabel:`Authorized Users`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:259
msgid ""
":guilabel:`People having some badges`: users who have been granted the "
"badges selected under :guilabel:`Required Badges`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`People having some badges`: user yang telah diberikan lencana "
"yang dipilih di bawah :guilabel:`Required Badges`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:262
msgid ""
"It is possible to restrict how many times per month each user can grant the "
"badge by enabling :guilabel:`Monthly Limited Sending` and entering "
"a :guilabel:`Limitation Number`."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk membatasi berapa kali per bulan setiap user dapat "
"memberikan badge dengan mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Monthly Limited Sending` dan "
"memasukkan :guilabel:`Limitation Number`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:266
msgid "Assign automatically"
msgstr "Tetapkan secara otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:268
msgid ""
"If the badge should be granted **automatically** when certain conditions are "
"met, select :guilabel:`No one, assigned through challenges` "
"under :guilabel:`Allowance to Grant`."
msgstr ""
"Jika badge harus diberikan **secara otomatis** ketika kondisi tertentu "
"terpenuhi, pilih :guilabel:`No one, assigned through challenges` di bawah "
":guilabel:`Allowance to Grant`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:271
msgid ""
"Next, determine how the badge should be granted by clicking :guilabel:`Add` "
"under the :guilabel:`Rewards for challenges` section. Select a challenge to "
"add it or create one by clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Selanjutnya, tentukan bagaimana badge harus diberikan dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`Add` di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Rewards for challenges`. Pilih "
"challenge untuk menambahkannya atau buat yang baru dengan mengklik "
":guilabel:`New`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:276
msgid ""
"It is possible to give the badge a :guilabel:`Forum Badge Level` "
"(:guilabel:`Bronze`, :guilabel:`Silver`, :guilabel:`Gold`) to give it more "
"or less importance."
msgstr ""
"Dimungkinkan untuk memberikan badge sebuah :guilabel:`Forum Badge Level` "
"(:guilabel:`Bronze`, :guilabel:`Silver`, :guilabel:`Gold`) untuk memberikan "
"lebih banyak atau lebih sedikit kepentingan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Default forum badges"
msgstr "Badge forum default"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:287
msgid "Users can use tags to filter forum posts."
msgstr "User dapat menggunakan tag untuk memfilter posting forum."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:289
msgid ""
"To manage tags, go to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Forum: "
"Tags`. Click :guilabel:`New` to create a tag and select the "
"related :guilabel:`Forum`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengelola tag, buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> "
"Forum: Tags`. Klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuat tag dan pilih "
":guilabel:`Forum` yang terkait."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:293
msgid ""
"Use the :guilabel:`Tags` section on the forum's sidebar to filter all "
"questions assigned to the selected tag. Click :guilabel:`View all` to "
"display all tags."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan bagian :guilabel:`Tags` di sidebar forum untuk memfilter semua "
"pertanyaan yang ditetapkan ke tag yang dipilih. Klik :guilabel:`View all` "
"untuk menampilkan semua tag."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:295
msgid ""
"New tags can be created when posting a new message, provided the user has "
"enough :ref:`karma points <forum/karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Tag baru dapat dibuat saat memposting pesan baru, asalkan user memiliki "
"cukup :ref:`karma points <forum/karma-related-rights>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:301
msgid "Use a forum"
msgstr "Gunakan forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:304
msgid ""
"Access to many functionalities depends on a user's :ref:`karma points <forum/"
"karma-related-rights>`."
msgstr ""
"Akses ke banyak fungsionalitas bergantung pada :ref:`karma points <forum/"
"karma-related-rights>` user."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:310
msgid "Post questions"
msgstr "Posting pertanyaan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:312
msgid ""
"To create a new post, access the forum's front end, click :guilabel:`New "
"Post`, and fill in the following:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat posting baru, akses front end forum, klik :guilabel:`New "
"Post`, dan isi hal berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:315
msgid ":guilabel:`Title`: add the question or the topic of the post."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Title`: tambahkan pertanyaan atau topik posting."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:316
msgid ":guilabel:`Description`: add a description for the question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Description`: tambahkan deskripsi untuk pertanyaan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:317
msgid ":guilabel:`Tags`: add up to five :ref:`tags <forum/tags>`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tags`: tambahkan hingga lima :ref:`tags <forum/tags>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:319
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Post Your Question`."
msgstr "Klik :guilabel:`Post Your Question`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:324
msgid "Interact with posts"
msgstr "Berinteraksi dengan posting"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:326
msgid "Different actions are possible on a post."
msgstr "Berbagai tindakan dimungkinkan pada sebuah posting."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:328
msgid ""
"Mark a question as **favorite** by clicking the star button (:guilabel:`☆`)."
msgstr ""
"Tandai pertanyaan sebagai **favorit** dengan mengklik tombol bintang "
"(:guilabel:`☆`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:329
msgid ""
"Follow a post and get **notifications** (by email or within Odoo) when it is "
"answered by clicking the bell button (:guilabel:`🔔`)."
msgstr ""
"Ikuti postingan dan dapatkan **notifikasi** (melalui email atau dalam Odoo) "
"ketika dijawab dengan mengklik tombol lonceng (:guilabel:`🔔`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:331
msgid ""
"**Vote** *for* (up arrow :guilabel:`▲`) or *against* (down "
"arrow :guilabel:`▼`) a question or answer."
msgstr ""
"**Vote** *untuk* (panah atas :guilabel:`▲`) atau *menentang* (panah bawah "
":guilabel:`▼`) pertanyaan atau jawaban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:333
msgid ""
"Mark an answer as **best** by clicking the check mark button "
"(:guilabel:`✔`). This option is only available if the :guilabel:`Forum Mode` "
"is set to :guilabel:`Questions`."
msgstr ""
"Tandai jawaban sebagai **terbaik** dengan mengklik tombol tanda centang "
"(:guilabel:`✔`). Opsi ini hanya tersedia jika :guilabel:`Forum Mode` diatur "
"ke :guilabel:`Questions`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:335
msgid ":guilabel:`Answer` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Answer` pertanyaan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:336
msgid ""
"**Comment** on a question or answer by clicking the speech bubble button "
"(:guilabel:`💬`)."
msgstr ""
"**Komentar** pada pertanyaan atau jawaban dengan mengklik tombol gelembung "
"percakapan (:guilabel:`💬`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:337
msgid ""
"**Share** a question on Facebook, Twitter, or LinkedIn by clicking the "
"*share nodes* button."
msgstr ""
"**Bagikan** pertanyaan di Facebook, Twitter, atau LinkedIn dengan mengklik "
"tombol *share nodes*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:339
msgid "Click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`) to:"
msgstr "Klik tombol elipsis (:guilabel:`...`) untuk:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:341
msgid ":guilabel:`Edit` a question or answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Edit` pertanyaan atau jawaban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:342
msgid ":guilabel:`Close` a question."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Close` pertanyaan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:343
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete` a question, answer, or comment. It is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Undelete` questions afterward."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delete` pertanyaan, jawaban, atau komentar. Dimungkinkan untuk "
":guilabel:`Undelete` pertanyaan setelahnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:345
msgid ":guilabel:`Flag` a question or answer as offensive."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Flag` pertanyaan atau jawaban sebagai menyinggung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:346
msgid ":guilabel:`Convert` a comment into an answer."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Convert` komentar menjadi jawaban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:347
msgid ""
":guilabel:`View` the related :ref:`Helpdesk ticket <helpdesk/forum>`, if any."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`View` :ref:`tiket Pusat Bantuan <helpdesk/forum>` terkait, jika "
"ada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Posts actions"
msgstr "Tindakan postingan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:353
msgid ""
"By default, 150 karma points are required to view another user's profile. "
"This value can be configured when creating a new website."
msgstr ""
"Secara default, 150 poin karma diperlukan untuk melihat profil user lain. "
"Nilai ini dapat dikonfigurasi saat membuat website baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:359
msgid "Moderate a forum"
msgstr "Moderasi forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:361
msgid ""
"On the forum's front end, the sidebar's :guilabel:`Moderation tools` section "
"gathers the essential moderator functionalities."
msgstr ""
"Di front end forum, bagian :guilabel:`Moderation tools` pada sidebar "
"mengumpulkan fungsi-fungsi moderator yang penting."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Forum sidebar moderation tools"
msgstr "Alat moderasi sidebar forum"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:367
msgid ""
":guilabel:`To Validate`: access all questions and answers waiting for "
"validation before being displayed to non-moderator users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`To Validate`: akses semua pertanyaan dan jawaban yang menunggu "
"validasi sebelum ditampilkan kepada user non-moderator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Question to validate"
msgstr "Pertanyaan untuk divalidasi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:374
msgid ""
"A question is pending if a user does not have the required karma. The user "
"is not able to post questions or answers while awaiting validation. Only one "
"pending question per user is allowed per forum."
msgstr ""
"Pertanyaan tertunda jika user tidak memiliki karma yang diperlukan. User "
"tidak dapat memposting pertanyaan atau jawaban saat menunggu validasi. Hanya "
"satu pertanyaan tertunda per user yang diizinkan per forum."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:378
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Flagged`: access all questions and answers that have been flagged "
"as offensive. Click :guilabel:`Accept` to remove the offensive flag "
"or :guilabel:`Offensive` to confirm it, then select a reason and "
"click :guilabel:`Mark as offensive`. The post is then hidden from users "
"without moderation rights, and 100 karma points are deducted from the "
"offending user's tally."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Flagged`: akses semua pertanyaan dan jawaban yang telah ditandai "
"sebagai ofensif. Klik :guilabel:`Accept` untuk menghapus tanda ofensif atau "
":guilabel:`Offensive` untuk mengonfirmasinya, kemudian pilih alasan dan klik "
":guilabel:`Mark as offensive`. Postingan kemudian disembunyikan dari user "
"tanpa hak moderasi, dan 100 poin karma dikurangi dari saldo user yang "
"melanggar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:None
msgid "Offensive reason selection"
msgstr "Pemilihan alasan ofensif"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:386
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Closed`: access all questions that have been closed. It is "
"possible to :guilabel:`Delete` or :guilabel:`Reopen` them. To close a "
"question, open it, click the ellipsis button (:guilabel:`...`), "
"then :guilabel:`Close`, select a :guilabel:`Close Reason`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Close post`. The post is then hidden from users without "
"moderation rights."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Closed`: akses semua pertanyaan yang telah ditutup. Dimungkinkan "
"untuk :guilabel:`Delete` atau :guilabel:`Reopen` pertanyaan tersebut. Untuk "
"menutup pertanyaan, buka pertanyaan, klik tombol ellipsis (:guilabel:`...`), "
"kemudian :guilabel:`Close`, pilih :guilabel:`Close Reason`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Close post`. Postingan kemudian disembunyikan dari user tanpa hak "
"moderasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:392
msgid ""
"When selecting :guilabel:`Spam or advertising` or :guilabel:`Contains "
"offensive or malicious remarks` as the reason, 100 karma points are deducted "
"from the poster's tally."
msgstr ""
"Ketika memilih :guilabel:`Spam or advertising` atau :guilabel:`Contains "
"offensive or malicious remarks` sebagai alasan, 100 poin karma dikurangi "
"dari saldo penulis postingan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:396
msgid ""
"Create and edit close reasons by going to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Close Reasons`. Select :guilabel:`Basic` "
"as :guilabel:`Reason Type` if the reason should be used when closing a "
"question, and :guilabel:`Offensive` if it should be used for flagged posts."
msgstr ""
"Buat dan edit alasan penutupan dengan membuka :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Close Reasons`. Pilih :guilabel:`Basic` sebagai "
":guilabel:`Reason Type` jika alasan tersebut harus digunakan saat menutup "
"pertanyaan, dan :guilabel:`Offensive` jika harus digunakan untuk postingan "
"yang ditandai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/forum.rst:399
msgid ""
"Manage all posts by going to :menuselection:`Website  --> Configuration --> "
"Forum: Forums`, selecting the forum, and clicking the :guilabel:`Posts` "
"smart button. By clicking the :guilabel:`Actions` button, it is possible "
"to :guilabel:`Export`, :guilabel:`Archive`, :guilabel:`Unarchive`, "
"or :guilabel:`Delete` one or multiple posts."
msgstr ""
"Kelola semua postingan dengan membuka :menuselection:`Website  --> "
"Configuration --> Forum: Forums`, pilih forum, dan klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Posts`. Dengan mengklik tombol :guilabel:`Actions`, dimungkinkan "
"untuk :guilabel:`Export`, :guilabel:`Archive`, :guilabel:`Unarchive`, atau "
":guilabel:`Delete` satu atau beberapa postingan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:5
msgid "Live Chat"
msgstr "Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** allows users to communicate with website visitors in real-"
"time. With **Live Chat**, leads can be qualified for their sales potential, "
"support questions can be answered in real time, and issues can be directed "
"to the appropriate team for further investigation or follow up. **Live "
"Chat** also provides the opportunity for instant feedback from customers."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** memungkinkan user berkomunikasi dengan pengunjung website "
"secara real-time. Dengan **Live Chat**, prospek dapat dikualifikasi "
"berdasarkan potensi penjualan, pertanyaan dukungan dapat dijawab secara real-"
"time, dan masalah dapat diarahkan ke tim yang sesuai untuk investigasi atau "
"tindak lanjut lebih lanjut. **Live Chat** juga memberikan kesempatan untuk "
"mendapatkan umpan balik instan dari pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:13
msgid "Enable Live Chat"
msgstr "Aktifkan Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:15
msgid "The **Live Chat** application can be installed multiple ways:"
msgstr "Aplikasi **Live Chat** dapat diinstal dengan beberapa cara:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:17
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Apps application`, search `Live Chat`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Apps application`, cari `Live Chat`, dan klik "
":guilabel:`Install`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:18
msgid ""
"Go to the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams` "
"list view, select a team, and on the team's settings page, click the "
"checkbox next to :guilabel:`Live Chat`, under the :guilabel:`Channels` "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Buka tampilan daftar :menuselection:`Helpdesk app --> Configuration --> "
"Helpdesk Teams`, pilih tim, dan pada halaman pengaturan tim, centang kotak "
"di sebelah :guilabel:`Live Chat`, di bawah bagian :guilabel:`Channels`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:21
msgid ""
"In the :menuselection:`Website` app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Email & Marketing` section, check the "
"box next to :guilabel:`Livechat`, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi :menuselection:`Website`, buka :menuselection:`Configuration --> "
"Settings`, gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Email & Marketing`, centang kotak di "
"sebelah :guilabel:`Livechat`, dan klik :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of the settings page and the live chat feature for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan halaman pengaturan dan fitur live chat untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:29
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application is installed, a live chat *Channel* is "
"created, by default."
msgstr ""
"Setelah aplikasi **Live Chat** diinstal, sebuah *Channel* live chat dibuat "
"secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:32
msgid "Create live chat channels"
msgstr "Buat channel live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:34
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat *Channel*, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat "
"app`. Then, click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank channel detail form. Enter "
"the name of the new channel in the :guilabel:`Channel Name` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat *Channel* live chat baru, buka :menuselection:`Live Chat app`. "
"Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`New` untuk membuka formulir detail channel kosong. "
"Masukkan nama channel baru di bidang :guilabel:`Channel Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:38
msgid ""
"To configure the remaining tabs on the channel detail form (:ref:`Operators "
"<livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Options <livechat/options-"
"tab>`, :ref:`Channel Rules <livechat/channel-rules-tab>`, and :ref:`Widget "
"<livechat/widget-tab>`), follow the steps below."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi tab yang tersisa pada formulir detail channel "
"(:ref:`Operators <livechat/operators-tab>`, :ref:`Options <livechat/options-"
"tab>`, :ref:`Channel Rules <livechat/channel-rules-tab>`, dan :ref:`Widget "
"<livechat/widget-tab>`), ikuti langkah-langkah di bawah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a live chat channel form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan formulir channel live chat untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:46
msgid ""
"The channel detail form for any channel can be accessed by navigating back "
"to the :guilabel:`Website Live Chat Channels` dashboard, via the "
"breadcrumbs. Find the Kanban card for the appropriate live chat channel, "
"hover over it, and then click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the drop-down menu. "
"Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"Formulir detail channel untuk channel mana pun dapat diakses dengan kembali "
"ke dashboard :guilabel:`Website Live Chat Channels`, melalui breadcrumb. "
"Temukan kartu Kanban untuk channel live chat yang sesuai, arahkan kursor ke "
"atasnya, lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(ellipsis vertikal)"
"` untuk membuka menu drop-down. Klik :guilabel:`Configure Channel` untuk "
"membuka formulir detail channel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:55
msgid "Operators tab"
msgstr "Tab operator"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who act as agents and respond to live chat "
"requests from customers. When a user is added as an operator in a live chat "
"channel, they can receive chats from website visitors wherever they are in "
"the database. Chat windows open in the bottom-right corner of the screen."
msgstr ""
"*Operator* adalah user yang bertindak sebagai agen dan merespons permintaan "
"live chat dari pelanggan. Ketika user ditambahkan sebagai operator di "
"channel live chat, mereka dapat menerima chat dari pengunjung website di "
"mana pun mereka berada di database. Jendela chat terbuka di pojok kanan "
"bawah layar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "A live chat pop-up window in an Odoo database."
msgstr "Jendela pop-up live chat di database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:64
msgid ""
"On the channel detail form, click the :guilabel:`Operators` tab. The user "
"who originally created the live chat channel has been added as an operator "
"by default."
msgstr ""
"Pada formulir detail channel, klik tab :guilabel:`Operators`. User yang "
"awalnya membuat channel live chat telah ditambahkan sebagai operator secara "
"default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:68
msgid ""
"Current operators can be edited, or removed, by clicking on their respective "
"boxes in the :guilabel:`Operators` tab, which reveals a "
"separate :guilabel:`Open: Operators` pop-up. In that pop-up, adjust any "
"information, as needed. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`, or "
"click :guilabel:`Remove` to remove that operator from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Operator saat ini dapat diedit, atau dihapus, dengan mengklik kotak masing-"
"masing di tab :guilabel:`Operators`, yang menampilkan pop-up "
":guilabel:`Open: Operators` terpisah. Dalam pop-up tersebut, sesuaikan "
"informasi apa pun sesuai kebutuhan. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Save`, atau "
"klik :guilabel:`Remove` untuk menghapus operator tersebut dari channel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:73
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add` to reveal an :guilabel:`Add: Operators` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Add` untuk menampilkan jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Add: "
"Operators`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, scroll to find the desired users, or enter their name "
"in the search bar. Then, tick the checkbox next to the users to be added, "
"and click :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"Di jendela pop-up, gulir untuk menemukan user yang diinginkan, atau masukkan "
"nama mereka di bilah pencarian. Kemudian, centang kotak di sebelah user yang "
"akan ditambahkan, dan klik :guilabel:`Select`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:78
msgid ""
"New operators can be created and added to the list directly from this pop-up "
"window, as well, by clicking :guilabel:`New`, and filling out "
"the :guilabel:`Create Operators` form. When the form is complete, "
"click :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or :guilabel:`Save & New` for multiple "
"record creations."
msgstr ""
"Operator baru dapat dibuat dan ditambahkan ke daftar langsung dari jendela "
"pop-up ini juga, dengan mengklik :guilabel:`New`, dan mengisi formulir "
":guilabel:`Create Operators`. Setelah formulir selesai, klik :guilabel:`Save "
"& Close`, atau :guilabel:`Save & New` untuk pembuatan beberapa record."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:83
msgid ""
"Creating a new user can impact the status of an Odoo subscription, as the "
"total number of users in a database counts towards the billing rate. Proceed "
"with caution before creating a new user. If a user already exists, adding "
"them as an operator will **not** alter the subscription or billing rate for "
"a database."
msgstr ""
"Membuat user baru dapat memengaruhi status langganan Odoo, karena total "
"jumlah user dalam database dihitung dalam tarif tagihan. Lanjutkan dengan "
"hati-hati sebelum membuat user baru. Jika user sudah ada, menambahkan mereka "
"sebagai operator **tidak** akan mengubah langganan atau tarif tagihan untuk "
"database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:93
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab on the live chat channel detail form contains "
"the visual and text settings for the live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Options` pada formulir detail channel live chat berisi "
"pengaturan visual dan teks untuk jendela live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:99
msgid "Livechat button"
msgstr "Tombol Livechat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:101
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website."
msgstr "*Tombol Livechat* adalah ikon yang muncul di pojok kanan bawah website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:103
msgid ""
"Change the text in the :guilabel:`Notification text` field to update the "
"greeting displayed in the text bubble when the live chat button appears on "
"the website."
msgstr ""
"Ubah teks di bidang :guilabel:`Notification text` untuk memperbarui salam "
"yang ditampilkan dalam gelembung teks ketika tombol live chat muncul di "
"website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:106
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Button Color` alters the color of the live chat "
"button as it appears on the website. To change the color, click on a color "
"bubble to open the color selection window, then click and drag the circle "
"along the color gradient. Click out of the selection window once complete. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon to the right of the "
"color bubbles to reset the colors to the default selection."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color` mengubah warna tombol live chat yang "
"muncul di website. Untuk mengubah warna, klik gelembung warna untuk membuka "
"jendela pemilihan warna, lalu klik dan seret lingkaran sepanjang gradien "
"warna. Klik di luar jendela pemilihan setelah selesai. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` di sebelah kanan gelembung warna untuk "
"mengatur ulang warna ke pilihan default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:113
msgid ""
"Color selection, for the button or header, can be made manually using a "
"slider or through RGB, HSL, or HEX color code entries from the pop-up color "
"selection window that appears when either of the color bubbles are clicked. "
"Different options are available, depending on the operating system."
msgstr ""
"Pemilihan warna, untuk tombol atau header, dapat dilakukan secara manual "
"menggunakan slider atau melalui entri kode warna RGB, HSL, atau HEX dari "
"jendela pemilihan warna pop-up yang muncul ketika salah satu gelembung warna "
"diklik. Opsi yang berbeda tersedia, tergantung pada sistem operasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:119
msgid ""
"With the following settings, the live chat button appears on the website as "
"shown:"
msgstr ""
"Dengan pengaturan berikut, tombol live chat muncul di website seperti yang "
"ditampilkan:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Notification text`: \"Have a Question? Chat with us.\""
msgstr ":guilabel:`Notification text`: \"Have a Question? Chat with us.\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:122
msgid ":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color`: set to purple"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Livechat Button Color`: diatur ke ungu"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:0
msgid "View of an Odoo website emphasizing the livechat button."
msgstr "Tampilan website Odoo yang menekankan tombol livechat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:128
msgid "Livechat window"
msgstr "Jendela Livechat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:130
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Livechat Window` is the space where the live chat "
"conversation with website visitors takes place."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jendela Livechat` adalah ruang di mana percakapan live chat "
"dengan pengunjung website berlangsung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:133
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Welcome Message` to change the message a visitor sees "
"when they open a new chat session. This message appears as though it is sent "
"by a live chat operator, and acts as both a greeting and an invitation to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Edit :guilabel:`Pesan Selamat Datang` untuk mengubah pesan yang dilihat "
"pengunjung saat membuka sesi chat baru. Pesan ini muncul seolah-olah dikirim "
"oleh operator live chat, dan berfungsi sebagai sapaan sekaligus undangan "
"untuk melanjutkan percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:137
msgid ""
"Edit the :guilabel:`Chat Input Placeholder` to alter the text that appears "
"in the box where visitors type their replies. This message prompts the "
"visitor to initiate the chat."
msgstr ""
"Edit :guilabel:`Placeholder Input Chat` untuk mengubah teks yang muncul di "
"kotak tempat pengunjung mengetik balasan mereka. Pesan ini mendorong "
"pengunjung untuk memulai chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:140
msgid ""
"The *Channel Header* is the colored bar at the top of the chat window. "
"The :guilabel:`Channel Header Color` can be changed following the same steps "
"as the :ref:`Livechat button <livechat/livechat-button>`."
msgstr ""
"*Header Channel* adalah bilah berwarna di bagian atas jendela chat. "
":guilabel:`Warna Header Channel` dapat diubah dengan mengikuti langkah yang "
"sama seperti :ref:`tombol Livechat <livechat/livechat-button>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid "The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text."
msgstr "Jendela live chat dengan header channel ungu dan teks placeholder."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:147
msgid ""
"The live chat window with a purple channel header and placeholder text that "
"reads, \"Say Something...\""
msgstr ""
"Jendela live chat dengan header channel ungu dan teks placeholder yang "
"berbunyi, \"Katakan Sesuatu...\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:153
msgid "Channel Rules tab"
msgstr "Tab Aturan Channel"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:155
msgid ""
"To configure which website user actions open the live chat window, go to "
"the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab on the live chat channel detail form."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengonfigurasi tindakan pengguna website mana yang membuka jendela "
"live chat, buka tab :guilabel:`Aturan Channel` pada formulir detail channel "
"live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:158
msgid ""
"To create a new channel rule, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. This opens "
"the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat aturan channel baru, klik :guilabel:`Tambahkan baris`. Ini "
"akan membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat Aturan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of a channel's rules form for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan formulir aturan channel untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:165
msgid "Create new rules"
msgstr "Buat aturan baru"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:167
msgid ""
"Fill out the fields on the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window as "
"instructed below, then click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Isi kolom-kolom pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Buat Aturan` seperti yang "
"diinstruksikan di bawah ini, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Simpan & Tutup`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:172
msgid "Live Chat Button"
msgstr "Tombol Live Chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:174
msgid ""
"The *Livechat Button* is the icon that appears in the bottom-right corner of "
"the website. Select from one of the following display options:"
msgstr ""
"*Tombol Livechat* adalah ikon yang muncul di sudut kanan bawah website. "
"Pilih salah satu opsi tampilan berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:177
msgid ":guilabel:`Show`: displays the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tampilkan`: menampilkan tombol chat pada halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:178
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Show with notification`: displays the chat button, as well as a "
"floating text bubble next to the button."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Tampilkan dengan notifikasi`: menampilkan tombol chat, serta "
"gelembung teks mengambang di sebelah tombol."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:180
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Open automatically`: displays the button, and automatically opens "
"the chat window after a specified amount of time (designated in "
"the :guilabel:`Open automatically timer` field, that appears when this "
"option is selected)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Buka secara otomatis`: menampilkan tombol, dan otomatis membuka "
"jendela chat setelah jangka waktu tertentu (ditentukan dalam kolom "
":guilabel:`Timer buka otomatis`, yang muncul saat opsi ini dipilih)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:183
msgid ":guilabel:`Hide`: hides the chat button on the page."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Sembunyikan`: menyembunyikan tombol chat pada halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:185
msgid "Chatbot"
msgstr "Chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:187
msgid ""
"To include a :doc:`Chatbot <livechat/chatbots>` on this channel, select it "
"from the drop-down menu. If the chatbot should only be active when no "
"operators are active, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no "
"operator`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyertakan :doc:`Chatbot <livechat/chatbots>` pada channel ini, pilih "
"dari menu drop-down. Jika chatbot hanya aktif saat tidak ada operator yang "
"aktif, centang kotak berlabel :guilabel:`Diaktifkan hanya jika tidak ada "
"operator`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:191
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator` field is **only** visible if a "
"chatbot is selected in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Diaktifkan hanya jika tidak ada operator` **hanya** "
"terlihat jika chatbot dipilih dalam kolom :guilabel:`Chatbot`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:194
msgid "URL Regex"
msgstr "URL Regex"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:196
msgid ""
"The *URL Regex* specifies the web pages where this rule should be applied. "
"In the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field, input the relative URL of the page where "
"the chat button should appear."
msgstr ""
"*URL Regex* menentukan halaman web tempat aturan ini diterapkan. Di kolom "
":guilabel:`URL Regex`, masukkan URL relatif halaman tempat tombol chat akan "
"muncul."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:200
msgid ""
"For example, to apply the rule to the URL, `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/"
"shop`, enter `/shop` to the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"Misalnya, untuk menerapkan aturan pada URL `https://mydatabse.odoo.com/"
"shop`, masukkan `/shop` ke kolom :guilabel:`URL Regex`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:203
msgid ""
"To apply the rule to *all* pages on the database, enter `/` in "
"the :guilabel:`URL Regex` field."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menerapkan aturan ke *semua* halaman di database, masukkan `/` di "
"kolom :guilabel:`URL Regex`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:206
msgid "Open automatically timer"
msgstr "Timer buka otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:208
msgid ""
"This field designates the amount of time (in seconds) a page should be open "
"before the chat window opens. This field **only** appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Button` for this rule is set to :guilabel:`Open "
"automatically`."
msgstr ""
"Kolom ini menunjukkan jumlah waktu (dalam detik) sebuah halaman harus "
"terbuka sebelum jendela chat terbuka. Kolom ini **hanya** muncul jika "
":guilabel:`Tombol Live Chat` untuk aturan ini diatur ke :guilabel:`Buka "
"secara otomatis`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:212
msgid "Country"
msgstr "Negara"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:214
msgid ""
"If this channel should **only** be available to site visitors in specific "
"countries, add them to the :guilabel:`Country` field. If this field is left "
"blank, the channel is available to all site visitors, regardless of location."
msgstr ""
"Jika saluran ini **hanya** tersedia untuk pengunjung situs di negara "
"tertentu, tambahkan mereka ke kolom :guilabel:`Negara`. Jika kolom ini "
"dibiarkan kosong, saluran tersedia untuk semua pengunjung situs, terlepas "
"dari lokasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:219
msgid ""
"In order to track the geographical location of visitors, *GeoIP* **must** be "
"installed on the database. While this feature is installed by default on "
"*Odoo Online* databases, *On-Premise* databases require "
"additional :doc:`setup steps </administration/on_premise/geo_ip>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melacak lokasi geografis pengunjung, *GeoIP* **harus** diinstal di "
"database. Meskipun fitur ini diinstal secara default di database *Odoo "
"Online*, database *On-Premise* memerlukan :doc:`langkah-langkah pengaturan </"
"administration/on_premise/geo_ip>` tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:226
msgid "Widget tab"
msgstr "Tab Widget"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:228
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Widget` tab on the live chat channel detail form provides an "
"embeddable code snippet for external, non-Odoo websites. This code can be "
"added to a website to provide access to a live chat window."
msgstr ""
"Tab :guilabel:`Widget` pada formulir detail saluran live chat menyediakan "
"kode yang dapat disematkan untuk situs web eksternal non-Odoo. Kode ini "
"dapat ditambahkan ke situs web untuk menyediakan akses ke jendela live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:233
msgid ""
"The live chat widget can be added to websites created through Odoo by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Website app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Then, scroll to the :menuselection:`Email & Marketing` section. In "
"the :guilabel:`Channel` field, select the channel to add to the site. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save` to apply."
msgstr ""
"Widget live chat dapat ditambahkan ke situs web yang dibuat melalui Odoo "
"dengan membuka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Website --> Konfigurasi --> "
"Pengaturan`. Kemudian, gulir ke bagian :menuselection:`Email & Pemasaran`. "
"Di kolom :guilabel:`Saluran`, pilih saluran yang akan ditambahkan ke situs. "
"Klik :guilabel:`Simpan` untuk menerapkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:238
msgid ""
"To add the widget to a website created on a third-party platform, click the "
"first :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on the :guilabel:`Widget` "
"tab, and paste the code into the `<head>` tag on the site."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan widget ke situs web yang dibuat di platform pihak ketiga, "
"klik ikon :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(salin)` pertama di tab "
":guilabel:`Widget`, dan tempelkan kodenya ke dalam tag `<head>` di situs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:242
msgid ""
"Likewise, to send a live chat session to a customer, click the "
"second :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon on "
"the :guilabel:`Widget` tab. This link can be sent directly to a customer. "
"When they click the link, they are redirected to a new chat window."
msgstr ""
"Demikian pula, untuk mengirim sesi live chat ke pelanggan, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`(salin)` kedua di tab :guilabel:`Widget`. "
"Tautan ini dapat dikirim langsung ke pelanggan. Ketika mereka mengklik "
"tautan tersebut, mereka akan diarahkan ke jendela chat baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:None
msgid "View of the widget tab for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan tab widget untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:250
msgid ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:251
msgid ":doc:`livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:252
msgid ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/ratings`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:253
msgid ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/chatbots`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat.rst:254
msgid ":doc:`livechat/participate`"
msgstr ":doc:`livechat/participate`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:3
msgid "Chatbots"
msgstr "Chatbot-Chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *Chatbot* is a program designed to mimic a conversation with a live human. "
"Chatbots are assigned a script of pre-written steps to follow. The scripts "
"are designed to anticipate a visitor's potential response, and lead them "
"through a series of questions and answers the same way a live team member "
"would."
msgstr ""
"*Chatbot* adalah program yang dirancang untuk meniru percakapan dengan "
"manusia langsung. Chatbot diberi skrip langkah-langkah yang telah ditulis "
"sebelumnya untuk diikuti. Skrip dirancang untuk mengantisipasi respons "
"potensial pengunjung, dan memandu mereka melalui serangkaian pertanyaan dan "
"jawaban dengan cara yang sama seperti yang dilakukan anggota tim langsung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:10
msgid ""
"Chatbots can be customized to fill various roles, from customer support, to "
"creating leads, to collecting contact information. The goal of each chatbot "
"can vary based on several criteria, including the webpage where it is "
"located, and the information it captures."
msgstr ""
"Chatbot dapat disesuaikan untuk mengisi berbagai peran, mulai dari dukungan "
"pelanggan, hingga membuat prospek, hingga mengumpulkan informasi kontak. "
"Tujuan setiap chatbot dapat bervariasi berdasarkan beberapa kriteria, "
"termasuk halaman web tempat chatbot berada dan informasi yang ditangkapnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of the chat window with a helpdesk ticket created in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan jendela chat dengan tiket Pusat Bantuan yang dibuat di Odoo Live "
"Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:20
msgid "Build a chatbot"
msgstr "Membangun chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:22
msgid ""
"Before creating a new chatbot, the **Live Chat** application must first "
"be :ref:`installed <general/install>`."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum membuat chatbot baru, aplikasi **Live Chat** harus :ref:`diinstal "
"<general/install>` terlebih dahulu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:25
msgid ""
"After the **Live Chat** application has been installed on the database, go "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah aplikasi **Live Chat** diinstal pada database, buka "
":menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:29
msgid ""
"When the **Live Chat** app is installed, a sample chatbot is created, named "
"*Welcome Bot*. This chatbot has a preconfigured script that walks through a "
"few basic steps, including asking for a visitor's email address, and "
"forwarding the conversation to an operator."
msgstr ""
"Ketika aplikasi **Live Chat** diinstal, chatbot contoh dibuat dengan nama "
"*Welcome Bot*. Chatbot ini memiliki skrip yang telah dikonfigurasi "
"sebelumnya yang menjalankan beberapa langkah dasar, termasuk meminta alamat "
"email pengunjung dan meneruskan percakapan ke operator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:33
msgid ""
"*Welcome Bot* can be used as a starting point. The existing steps can be "
"edited or removed, and new steps can be added to customize the script, as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"*Welcome Bot* dapat digunakan sebagai titik awal. Langkah-langkah yang ada "
"dapat diedit atau dihapus, dan langkah baru dapat ditambahkan untuk "
"menyesuaikan skrip sesuai kebutuhan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:36
msgid "*Welcome Bot* can be deleted or archived, if necessary."
msgstr "*Welcome Bot* dapat dihapus atau diarsipkan jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the Welcome Bot script in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan skrip Welcome Bot di Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:41
msgid ""
"To create a new chatbot, navigate to the :guilabel:`Chatbot` page "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`) and "
"click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank chatbot details page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat chatbot baru, navigasikan ke halaman :guilabel:`Chatbot` "
"(:menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`) dan klik "
":guilabel:`New` untuk membuka halaman detail chatbot kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:44
msgid ""
"Enter a name in the :guilabel:`Chatbot Name` field and hover over the image "
"on the right. Click on the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon that "
"appears to add a photo."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan nama di kolom :guilabel:`Chatbot Name` dan arahkan kursor ke gambar "
"di sebelah kanan. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pensil)` yang "
"muncul untuk menambahkan foto."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:48
msgid "Chatbot scripts"
msgstr "Skrip chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:50
msgid ""
"After the new chatbot has been created and named, the next step is to create "
"a script. Chatbot conversations follow an accompanying script, comprised of "
"lines of dialog. Each line is designed to either deliver or capture "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Setelah chatbot baru dibuat dan diberi nama, langkah selanjutnya adalah "
"membuat skrip. Percakapan chatbot mengikuti skrip yang menyertainya, terdiri "
"dari baris-baris dialog. Setiap baris dirancang untuk menyampaikan atau "
"menangkap informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:54
msgid ""
"To create a chatbot script, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` in "
"the :guilabel:`Script` tab of the chatbot detail page, and "
"a :guilabel:`Create Script Steps` pop-up window appears. This form must be "
"filled out for each line of text (dialog) that the chatbot could potentially "
"deliver during the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat skrip chatbot, klik :guilabel:`Add a Line` di tab "
":guilabel:`Script` pada halaman detail chatbot, dan jendela pop-up "
":guilabel:`Create Script Steps` akan muncul. Formulir ini harus diisi untuk "
"setiap baris teks (dialog) yang berpotensi disampaikan chatbot selama "
"percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:59
msgid ""
"First, enter the content of the message in the :guilabel:`Message` field. "
"Then, select an option from the :guilabel:`Step Type` and :ref:`Only If "
"<livechat/chatbots/only-if>` drop-down menus."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, masukkan konten pesan di kolom :guilabel:`Message`. Kemudian, pilih "
"opsi dari menu drop-down :guilabel:`Step Type` dan :ref:`Only If <livechat/"
"chatbots/only-if>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:63
msgid "Step types"
msgstr "Jenis langkah"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:65
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Step Type` selected depends on the intended purpose of the "
"message. The available options in the :guilabel:`Step Type` drop-down menu "
"are detailed below."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Step Type` yang dipilih tergantung pada tujuan pesan yang "
"dimaksudkan. Opsi yang tersedia di menu drop-down :guilabel:`Step Type` "
"dijelaskan di bawah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:69
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Teks"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:71
msgid ""
"This step is used for messages where no answer is expected or necessary. "
"Text steps can be used for greetings, to offer resources, such as "
"documentation, or provide links to specific web pages."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini digunakan untuk pesan di mana tidak ada jawaban yang diharapkan "
"atau diperlukan. Langkah teks dapat digunakan untuk salam, menawarkan sumber "
"daya seperti dokumentasi, atau menyediakan tautan ke halaman web tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:75
msgid ""
"*Text* step types are only intended to deliver information, and do not allow "
"for any visitor input. As such, they must be followed by additional steps to "
"continue the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Jenis langkah *Text* hanya dimaksudkan untuk menyampaikan informasi, dan "
"tidak memungkinkan input pengunjung. Oleh karena itu, langkah ini harus "
"diikuti dengan langkah tambahan untuk melanjutkan percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:79
msgid "Question"
msgstr "Pertanyaan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:81
msgid ""
"This step asks a question and provides a set of answers. The visitor clicks "
"on one answer, which either leads to a new step in the conversation, or can "
"lead to an optional link to a new webpage."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini mengajukan pertanyaan dan menyediakan serangkaian jawaban. "
"Pengunjung mengklik satu jawaban, yang mengarah ke langkah baru dalam "
"percakapan, atau dapat mengarah ke tautan opsional ke halaman web baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:84
msgid ""
"Enter the question in the :guilabel:`Message` field. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Answer` heading, click :guilabel:`Add a Line` to create a "
"blank answer line."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan pertanyaan di kolom :guilabel:`Message`. Kemudian, di bawah judul "
":guilabel:`Answer`, klik :guilabel:`Add a Line` untuk membuat baris jawaban "
"kosong."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:87
msgid ""
"Proceed to enter the answer as it should appear to the visitor. To turn the "
"answer into a link that redirects the visitor when selected, add the URL to "
"the answer line under the :guilabel:`Optional Link` heading."
msgstr ""
"Lanjutkan dengan memasukkan jawaban seperti yang seharusnya muncul kepada "
"pengunjung. Untuk mengubah jawaban menjadi tautan yang mengarahkan "
"pengunjung saat dipilih, tambahkan URL ke baris jawaban di bawah judul "
":guilabel:`Optional Link`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:91
msgid ""
"Repeat these steps for every answer to be included for the question. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & Close` or :guilabel:`Save & New` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Ulangi langkah-langkah ini untuk setiap jawaban yang akan disertakan untuk "
"pertanyaan tersebut. Klik :guilabel:`Save & Close` atau :guilabel:`Save & "
"New` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:95
msgid ""
"It is helpful to add a catchall answer to question steps (e.g: `Something "
"else`). This helps visitors continue the conversation, even if their needs "
"do not fit with any of the other answers."
msgstr ""
"Akan sangat membantu untuk menambahkan jawaban penampung semua ke langkah "
"pertanyaan (misalnya: `Sesuatu yang lain`). Ini membantu pengunjung "
"melanjutkan percakapan, bahkan jika kebutuhan mereka tidak sesuai dengan "
"jawaban lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:99
msgid "Email"
msgstr "Email"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:101
msgid ""
"This step prompts visitors to provide their email address, which is stored "
"and can be used by team members later to follow up with additional "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini meminta pengunjung untuk memberikan alamat email mereka, yang "
"disimpan dan dapat digunakan oleh anggota tim nanti untuk menindaklanjuti "
"dengan informasi tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:104
msgid ""
"The only accepted inputs for this step type are email addresses that are in "
"a valid format. If a visitor attempts to enter anything other than a valid "
"email address, the chatbot responds with a message stating it does not "
"recognize the information submitted."
msgstr ""
"Satu-satunya input yang diterima untuk jenis langkah ini adalah alamat email "
"yang dalam format yang valid. Jika pengunjung mencoba memasukkan apa pun "
"selain alamat email yang valid, chatbot merespons dengan pesan yang "
"menyatakan bahwa ia tidak mengenali informasi yang dikirimkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of a chatbot responding to an invalid email."
msgstr "Tampilan chatbot yang merespons email yang tidak valid."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:112
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "Telepon"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:114
msgid ""
"Similar to email, this step type prompts the visitor to enter their phone "
"number, which can be used to follow up with additional information, schedule "
"demos, and more."
msgstr ""
"Mirip dengan email, jenis langkah ini meminta pengunjung untuk memasukkan "
"nomor telepon mereka, yang dapat digunakan untuk menindaklanjuti dengan "
"informasi tambahan, menjadwalkan demo, dan lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:118
msgid ""
"Due to the vast number of formats used for phone numbers worldwide, "
"responses to this step type are not validated for formatting, and can "
"include both numbers and special characters."
msgstr ""
"Karena banyaknya format yang digunakan untuk nomor telepon di seluruh dunia, "
"respons terhadap jenis langkah ini tidak divalidasi untuk pemformatan, dan "
"dapat menyertakan angka dan karakter khusus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:124
msgid "Forward to Operator"
msgstr "Forward ke Operator"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:126
msgid ""
"This step forwards the conversation to an active live chat operator, so they "
"can continue assisting the visitor. As the conversation transcript is passed "
"on to the operator, they can pick up where the chatbot left off. This not "
"only saves time for all parties involved, it can also help qualify "
"conversations before they reach live operators."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini meneruskan percakapan ke operator live chat yang aktif, sehingga "
"mereka dapat terus membantu pengunjung. Karena transkrip percakapan "
"diteruskan ke operator, mereka dapat melanjutkan dari tempat chatbot "
"berhenti. Ini tidak hanya menghemat waktu untuk semua pihak yang terlibat, "
"tetapi juga dapat membantu mengkualifikasi percakapan sebelum mencapai "
"operator langsung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:132
msgid ""
"If no active operator is available on the channel, the chatbot continues the "
"conversation with the visitor. Therefore, additional steps should be added "
"after this one to ensure there is no abrupt end to the conversation. The "
"additional steps can both inform visitors about the lack of available "
"operators (e.g. `Uh-oh, it looks like none of our operators are available`) "
"and continue the conversation (e.g. `Would you like to leave your email "
"address?`)."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak ada operator aktif yang tersedia di channel, chatbot melanjutkan "
"percakapan dengan pengunjung. Oleh karena itu, langkah tambahan harus "
"ditambahkan setelah ini untuk memastikan tidak ada akhir percakapan yang "
"tiba-tiba. Langkah tambahan dapat menginformasikan pengunjung tentang "
"kurangnya operator yang tersedia (misalnya `Aduh, sepertinya tidak ada "
"operator kami yang tersedia`) dan melanjutkan percakapan (misalnya `Apakah "
"Anda ingin meninggalkan alamat email Anda?`)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid ""
"View of a chatbot follow up messages when no live chat operator is available."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan pesan tindak lanjut chatbot ketika tidak ada operator live chat "
"yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:142
msgid "Free Input/Multi-Line"
msgstr "Input Bebas/Multi-Baris"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:144
msgid ""
"The *free input* step allows visitors to respond to questions without "
"providing pre-written responses. Information provided in these responses is "
"stored in the chat transcripts."
msgstr ""
"Langkah *input bebas* memungkinkan pengunjung untuk merespons pertanyaan "
"tanpa memberikan respons yang telah ditulis sebelumnya. Informasi yang "
"diberikan dalam respons ini disimpan dalam transkrip obrolan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:147
msgid ""
"Choose between :guilabel:`Free Input` and :guilabel:`Free Input (Multi-"
"Line)` depending on the type and amount of information the visitor is asked "
"to provide."
msgstr ""
"Pilih antara :guilabel:`Free Input` dan :guilabel:`Free Input (Multi-Line)` "
"tergantung pada jenis dan jumlah informasi yang diminta untuk diberikan oleh "
"pengunjung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:151
msgid "Create Lead"
msgstr "Buat Lead"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:153
msgid ""
"This step creates a lead in the **CRM** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created lead to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini membuat prospek di aplikasi **CRM**. Pilih opsi dari bidang drop-"
"down :guilabel:`Sales Team` yang muncul untuk menetapkan prospek yang dibuat "
"ke tim tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:157
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini hanya tersedia jika aplikasi **CRM** diinstal pada database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:160
msgid "Create Ticket"
msgstr "Buat Tiket"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:162
msgid ""
"This step creates a :doc:`ticket <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` in the **Helpdesk** application. Select an option from "
"the :guilabel:`Helpdesk Team` drop-down field that appears to assign the "
"created ticket to a specific team."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini membuat :doc:`tiket <../../services/helpdesk/overview/"
"receiving_tickets>` di aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan**. Pilih opsi dari bidang "
"drop-down :guilabel:`Helpdesk Team` yang muncul untuk menetapkan tiket yang "
"dibuat ke tim tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:167
msgid ""
"This step is only available if the **Helpdesk** application is installed on "
"the database."
msgstr ""
"Langkah ini hanya tersedia jika aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan** diinstal pada "
"database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:172
msgid "Only if"
msgstr "Hanya jika"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:174
msgid ""
"Chatbot scripts operate on an if/then basis, which means the next question "
"presented to the visitor is determined by the answer provided to the "
"previous question."
msgstr ""
"Skrip chatbot beroperasi berdasarkan if/then, yang berarti pertanyaan "
"berikutnya yang disajikan kepada pengunjung ditentukan oleh jawaban yang "
"diberikan untuk pertanyaan sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:177
msgid ""
"To continue the progression of the conversation, the :guilabel:`Create "
"Script Steps` form for a new step contains a field labeled :guilabel:`Only "
"If`. This field is where the progression of questions are defined."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melanjutkan perkembangan percakapan, formulir :guilabel:`Create Script "
"Steps` untuk langkah baru berisi bidang berlabel :guilabel:`Only If`. Bidang "
"ini adalah tempat perkembangan pertanyaan didefinisikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:181
msgid ""
"If a step is intended to follow all of the previous messages, this field can "
"be left empty. However, if a message should only be sent conditionally, "
"based on a previous response, or several previous responses, those responses "
"**must** be added to this field."
msgstr ""
"Jika suatu langkah dimaksudkan untuk mengikuti semua pesan sebelumnya, "
"bidang ini dapat dibiarkan kosong. Namun, jika pesan hanya boleh dikirim "
"secara kondisional, berdasarkan respons sebelumnya, atau beberapa respons "
"sebelumnya, respons tersebut **harus** ditambahkan ke bidang ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:186
msgid ""
"If any selections are made in the :guilabel:`Only If` field, they must all "
"be selected during the conversation before this step is included. Only "
"include selections in this field if they are necessary for this step to be "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Jika ada pilihan yang dibuat di bidang :guilabel:`Hanya Jika`, semuanya "
"harus dipilih selama percakapan sebelum langkah ini disertakan. Hanya "
"sertakan pilihan di bidang ini jika diperlukan agar langkah ini ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:191
msgid ""
"In the *Welcome Bot* script, a visitor can ask about pricing information. If "
"the visitor selects this response, a step is included to forward the "
"conversation to an operator. The chatbot first sends a message informing the "
"visitor that it is checking to see if an operator is available to assist "
"with pricing information."
msgstr ""
"Dalam skrip *Welcome Bot*, pengunjung dapat menanyakan informasi harga. Jika "
"pengunjung memilih respons ini, langkah disertakan untuk meneruskan "
"percakapan ke operator. Chatbot pertama-tama mengirim pesan yang memberi "
"tahu pengunjung bahwa ia sedang memeriksa apakah ada operator yang tersedia "
"untuk membantu dengan informasi harga."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:196
msgid ""
"However, this message should only be delivered if the visitor requests "
"pricing information. In that situation, the conversation would proceed as "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Namun, pesan ini hanya boleh dikirim jika pengunjung meminta informasi "
"harga. Dalam situasi tersebut, percakapan akan berlanjut seperti di bawah "
"ini:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:199
msgid "Welcome Bot: \"*What are you looking for?*\""
msgstr "Welcome Bot: \"*Apa yang Anda cari?*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:200
msgid "Visitor: \"**I have a pricing question.**\""
msgstr "Pengunjung: \"**Saya punya pertanyaan tentang harga.**\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:201
msgid ""
"Welcome Bot: \"*Hmmm, let me check if I can find someone that could help you "
"with that...*\""
msgstr ""
"Welcome Bot: \"*Hmmm, biarkan saya periksa apakah saya dapat menemukan "
"seseorang yang bisa membantu Anda dengan itu...*\""

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:203
msgid ""
"In the details form for the :guilabel:`Text` step, the *I have a pricing "
"question* response has been selected in the :guilabel:`Only If` field. As "
"such, this step is only shown in conversations where that response has been "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Dalam formulir detail untuk langkah :guilabel:`Teks`, respons *Saya punya "
"pertanyaan tentang harga* telah dipilih di bidang :guilabel:`Hanya Jika`. "
"Dengan demikian, langkah ini hanya ditampilkan dalam percakapan di mana "
"respons tersebut telah dipilih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "View of the new message form emphasizing the Only If field."
msgstr "Tampilan formulir pesan baru yang menekankan bidang Hanya Jika."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:211
msgid "Script testing"
msgstr "Pengujian skrip"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:213
msgid ""
"To ensure all visitors have a satisfactory experience with the chatbot, each "
"message needs to lead to a natural conclusion. Chatbot scripts should be "
"tested to confirm there are no dead-ends, and to understand what the visitor "
"sees when they interact with the chatbot."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan semua pengunjung memiliki pengalaman yang memuaskan dengan "
"chatbot, setiap pesan perlu mengarah ke kesimpulan yang alami. Skrip chatbot "
"harus diuji untuk memastikan tidak ada jalan buntu, dan untuk memahami apa "
"yang dilihat pengunjung ketika mereka berinteraksi dengan chatbot."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:218
msgid ""
"If the visitor provides an answer, or input, that is not assigned a "
"corresponding follow-up response, the conversation stops (*dead-ends*). "
"Since the visitor cannot re-engage the chatbot, they must restart the "
"conversation by refreshing the chat window, or their browser. They may also "
"click on the :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the "
"message window."
msgstr ""
"Jika pengunjung memberikan jawaban, atau masukan, yang tidak diberi respons "
"tindak lanjut yang sesuai, percakapan berhenti (*jalan buntu*). Karena "
"pengunjung tidak dapat terlibat kembali dengan chatbot, mereka harus memulai "
"ulang percakapan dengan menyegarkan jendela obrolan, atau browser mereka. "
"Mereka juga dapat mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(segarkan)` di "
"bagian atas jendela pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:0
msgid "The refresh button at the top of the message window."
msgstr "Tombol segarkan di bagian atas jendela pesan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:226
msgid ""
"The :icon:`fa-refresh` (refresh) icon only appears when the chatbot script "
"has reached a dead-end."
msgstr ""
"Ikon :icon:`fa-refresh` (segarkan) hanya muncul ketika skrip chatbot telah "
"mencapai jalan buntu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:229
msgid ""
"To test the performance of a chatbot, first click on the :guilabel:`Test` "
"button at the top-left of the chatbot script page. Then, upon being "
"redirected to the testing screen, answer the chatbot prompts the same way a "
"potential site visitor would."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menguji kinerja chatbot, pertama-tama klik tombol :guilabel:`Uji` di "
"kiri atas halaman skrip chatbot. Kemudian, setelah dialihkan ke layar "
"pengujian, jawab prompt chatbot dengan cara yang sama seperti calon "
"pengunjung situs."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:233
msgid ""
"When the script has reached an end-point, the message *Conversation "
"ended...* appears at the bottom of the chat window. To begin the "
"conversation at the beginning of the script, click on the :icon:`fa-"
"refresh` :guilabel:`(refresh)` icon at the top of the message window. To "
"return to the script page, click :guilabel:`Back to edit mode` at the top of "
"the page."
msgstr ""
"Ketika skrip telah mencapai titik akhir, pesan *Percakapan berakhir...* "
"muncul di bagian bawah jendela obrolan. Untuk memulai percakapan dari awal "
"skrip, klik ikon :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`(segarkan)` di bagian atas "
"jendela pesan. Untuk kembali ke halaman skrip, klik :guilabel:`Kembali ke "
"mode edit` di bagian atas halaman."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:239
msgid "Add chatbot to a channel"
msgstr "Tambahkan chatbot ke kanal"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:241
msgid ""
"After a chatbot has been created and tested, it needs to be added to a live "
"chat channel."
msgstr ""
"Setelah chatbot dibuat dan diuji, chatbot perlu ditambahkan ke kanal Live "
"Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:243
msgid ""
"First, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat` application, find the Kanban card "
"for the appropriate live chat channel, hover over it, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon to open the "
"drop-down menu. Click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel "
"detail form."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, buka aplikasi :menuselection:`Live Chat`, temukan kartu Kanban "
"untuk kanal Live Chat yang sesuai, arahkan kursor ke atasnya, dan klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(elipsis vertikal)` untuk membuka menu "
"tarik-turun. Klik :guilabel:`Konfigurasi Kanal` untuk membuka formulir "
"detail kanal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:249
msgid ""
"To create a new live chat channel, open the :menuselection:`Live Chat app` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`. See :doc:`Live Chat <../livechat>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat kanal Live Chat baru, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi Live Chat` "
"dan klik :guilabel:`Baru`. Lihat :doc:`Live Chat <../livechat>` untuk "
"informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click on the :guilabel:`Channel Rules` tab. Then, open an existing rule, or "
"create a new one by clicking :guilabel:`Add a line`."
msgstr ""
"Klik tab :guilabel:`Channel Rules`. Kemudian, buka aturan yang sudah ada, "
"atau buat yang baru dengan mengklik :guilabel:`Add a line`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:255
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Rules` pop-up window, choose the appropriate "
"chatbot in the :guilabel:`Chatbot` field."
msgstr ""
"Pada jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Create Rules`, pilih chatbot yang sesuai di "
"bidang :guilabel:`Chatbot`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:258
msgid ""
"If the chatbot should only be active if there are no live chat operators "
"available, check the box labeled :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator`."
msgstr ""
"Jika chatbot hanya boleh aktif ketika tidak ada operator live chat yang "
"tersedia, centang kotak berlabel :guilabel:`Enabled only if no operator`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:None
msgid "View of the channel rules emphasizing the chatbot field."
msgstr "Tampilan aturan channel yang menekankan bidang chatbot."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/chatbots.rst:265
msgid ":doc:`Live chat channel rules </applications/websites/livechat>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Aturan channel live chat </applications/websites/livechat>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:3
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:118
msgid "Expertise"
msgstr "Keahlian"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo's **Live Chat**, agents can designate *expertise* in one or more "
"areas. This allows conversations to be assigned to them based on their scope "
"of knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Di **Live Chat** Odoo, agen dapat menetapkan *keahlian* di satu atau lebih "
"area. Ini memungkinkan percakapan ditetapkan kepada mereka berdasarkan "
"lingkup pengetahuan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:8
msgid ""
"When a visitor requests help on a specific topic, Odoo can automatically "
"assign the conversation to an available agent with that expertise. Expertise "
"improves routing efficiency, reduces wait time, and ensures customers speak "
"to the most qualified person available."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pengunjung meminta bantuan tentang topik tertentu, Odoo dapat secara "
"otomatis menetapkan percakapan kepada agen yang tersedia dengan keahlian "
"tersebut. Keahlian meningkatkan efisiensi routing, mengurangi waktu tunggu, "
"dan memastikan pelanggan berbicara dengan orang yang paling berkualifikasi "
"yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:13
msgid "Create a new expertise"
msgstr "Buat keahlian baru"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:15
msgid ""
"To create a new expertise, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Expertise` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter "
"a :guilabel:`Name` for the area of focus."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat keahlian baru, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Live "
"Chat --> Configuration --> Expertise` dan klik :guilabel:`New`. Masukkan "
":guilabel:`Name` untuk area fokus."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:18
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Operators`, select one or more users from the drop-down to "
"assign this expertise."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah :guilabel:`Operators`, pilih satu atau lebih user dari drop-down "
"untuk menetapkan keahlian ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:21
msgid ""
"*Administrator* level :doc:`access <../../general/users/access_rights>` is "
"required in the **Live Chat** application to create or edit expertise. Those "
"with *User* level access can view the expertise menu and see which users are "
"assigned to each expertise, but they cannot make changes."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Akses <../../general/users/access_rights>` level *Administrator* "
"diperlukan di aplikasi **Live Chat** untuk membuat atau mengedit keahlian. "
"Mereka yang memiliki akses level *User* dapat melihat menu keahlian dan "
"melihat user mana yang ditetapkan untuk setiap keahlian, tetapi mereka tidak "
"dapat membuat perubahan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:26
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:53
msgid "Set live chat expertise"
msgstr "Mengatur keahlian live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:28
msgid ""
"To set a user's live chat expertise, click on the user avatar in the top-"
"right corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Preferences` "
"from the drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, select one or more options from "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengatur keahlian live chat user, klik avatar user di pojok kanan atas "
"halaman mana pun di database. Pilih :guilabel:`My Preferences` dari menu "
"drop-down untuk membuka halaman profil. Di sisi kanan tab "
":guilabel:`Preferences`, pilih satu atau lebih opsi dari daftar drop-down "
":guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "A user profile with the Live Chat Expertise menu open."
msgstr "Profil user dengan menu Live Chat Expertise terbuka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:37
msgid "Forward conversations based on expertise"
msgstr "Teruskan percakapan berdasarkan keahlian"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once an expertise has been assigned to one or more operators, they can be "
"used to forward conversations. This allows a chatbot to identify the "
"operator who is best suited to handle a customer request."
msgstr ""
"Setelah keahlian ditetapkan kepada satu atau lebih operator, keahlian "
"tersebut dapat digunakan untuk meneruskan percakapan. Ini memungkinkan "
"chatbot mengidentifikasi operator yang paling sesuai untuk menangani "
"permintaan pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:44
msgid "Forward via chatbot"
msgstr "Teruskan melalui chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:46
msgid ""
":doc:`Chatbots <chatbots>` are designed to mimic a conversation with a live "
"human, and operate based on a pre-written script of steps to follow. "
"The :ref:`Forward to Operator <chatbot/forward-to-operator>` step type is "
"used to send a conversation from a chatbot to an active live chat agent who "
"can then continue the conversation based on where the chatbot left off. By "
"adding expertise to this step, the chatbot will first look for an agent with "
"matching expertise, to ensure the agent is the best person for the situation."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Chatbot <chatbots>` dirancang untuk meniru percakapan dengan manusia "
"langsung, dan beroperasi berdasarkan skrip langkah-langkah yang telah "
"ditulis sebelumnya. Tipe langkah :ref:`Teruskan ke Operator <chatbot/forward-"
"to-operator>` digunakan untuk mengirim percakapan dari chatbot ke agen live "
"chat aktif yang kemudian dapat melanjutkan percakapan berdasarkan di mana "
"chatbot berhenti. Dengan menambahkan keahlian ke langkah ini, chatbot akan "
"terlebih dahulu mencari agen dengan keahlian yang sesuai, untuk memastikan "
"agen adalah orang yang paling tepat untuk situasi tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:53
msgid ""
"To add expertise to a chatbot conversation, navigate to :menuselection:`Live "
"Chat app --> Configuration --> Chatbots`. Click on an existing chatbot to "
"open it, or click :guilabel:`New` to :ref:`create a new one <chatbot/build-a-"
"chatbot>`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan keahlian ke percakapan chatbot, buka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Live Chat --> Konfigurasi --> Chatbot`. Klik pada "
"chatbot yang ada untuk membukanya, atau klik :guilabel:`Baru` untuk "
":ref:`membuat yang baru <chatbot/build-a-chatbot>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:57
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Script` tab, if there is an existing *Forward to Operator* "
"step, click on it. If not, click :guilabel:`Add a line`, then select "
"*Forward to Operator* in the :guilabel:`Step Type` field."
msgstr ""
"Pada tab :guilabel:`Skrip`, jika ada langkah *Teruskan ke Operator* yang "
"sudah ada, klik pada langkah tersebut. Jika tidak, klik :guilabel:`Tambah "
"baris`, lalu pilih *Teruskan ke Operator* pada field :guilabel:`Tipe "
"Langkah`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:61
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Operator Expertise` field, select one or more expertise "
"for the chatbot to consider when prioritizing users for conversations on the "
"related channel. Click :guilabel:`Save` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Pada field :guilabel:`Keahlian Operator`, pilih satu atau lebih keahlian "
"untuk chatbot pertimbangkan saat memprioritaskan user untuk percakapan pada "
"saluran terkait. Klik :guilabel:`Simpan` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:66
msgid ""
"When making selections in this field, consider the use case for the chatbot. "
"A *Support* chatbot will cover different topics than a *Recruitment* chatbot."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat pilihan pada field ini, pertimbangkan kasus penggunaan untuk "
"chatbot. Chatbot *Dukungan* akan mencakup topik yang berbeda dari chatbot "
"*Perekrutan*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "A forward to operator script step pop-up."
msgstr "Pop-up langkah skrip teruskan ke operator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:73
msgid "Add users to a conversation"
msgstr "Tambahkan user ke percakapan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:75
msgid ""
"Users can add other live chat agents to an ongoing conversation directly "
"from the chat window. Open an active live chat conversation through "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. At the top-right of the chat, click "
"the :icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(user plus)` icon to open the *Invite "
"People* menu. The user's expertise is listed next to the :icon:`fa-"
"graduation-cap` :guilabel:`(graduation cap)` icon."
msgstr ""
"User dapat menambahkan agen live chat lain ke percakapan yang sedang "
"berlangsung langsung dari jendela obrolan. Buka percakapan live chat aktif "
"melalui :menuselection:`aplikasi Diskusi`. Di kanan atas obrolan, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-user-plus` :guilabel:`(user plus)` untuk membuka menu *Undang "
"Orang*. Keahlian user tercantum di sebelah ikon :icon:`fa-graduation-cap` "
":guilabel:`(topi wisuda)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid "The add users menu in a live chat conversation."
msgstr "Menu tambahkan user dalam percakapan live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:84
msgid ""
"To add a user to the conversation, tick the checkbox to the right of the "
"user's name, then click :guilabel:`Invite`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan user ke percakapan, centang kotak di sebelah kanan nama "
"user, lalu klik :guilabel:`Undang`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:88
msgid ""
"*Expertise* only appear on the *Invite People* pop-up for live chat "
"conversations, not direct messages."
msgstr ""
"*Keahlian* hanya muncul pada pop-up *Undang Orang* untuk percakapan live "
"chat, bukan pesan langsung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:92
msgid "Looking for help conversations"
msgstr "Percakapan mencari bantuan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:94
msgid ""
"In an active livechat conversation, the :ref:`Status <information/status>` "
"can be set to allow agents to identify conversations that require immediate "
"action, and inform other agents which conversations require their expertise "
"at any given time. If a conversation is marked with the status *Looking for "
"help*, other agents have the opportunity to join."
msgstr ""
"Dalam percakapan livechat aktif, :ref:`Status <information/status>` dapat "
"diatur untuk memungkinkan agen mengidentifikasi percakapan yang memerlukan "
"tindakan segera, dan memberi tahu agen lain percakapan mana yang memerlukan "
"keahlian mereka pada waktu tertentu. Jika percakapan ditandai dengan status "
"*Mencari bantuan*, agen lain memiliki kesempatan untuk bergabung."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:99
msgid ""
"To view *Looking for help* conversations, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. Conversations with the status appear under "
"the *Looking for help* heading."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat percakapan *Mencari bantuan*, buka :menuselection:`aplikasi "
"Diskusi`. Percakapan dengan status tersebut muncul di bawah judul *Mencari "
"bantuan*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:102
msgid ""
"If an agent has a matching expertise, the conversation is marked with "
"a :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(star)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Jika agen memiliki keahlian yang sesuai, percakapan ditandai dengan ikon "
":icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(bintang)`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:None
msgid ""
"A conversation with the looking for help status and relevant expertise "
"tagged."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan dengan status mencari bantuan dan keahlian relevan yang ditandai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:109
msgid ""
"*Looking for help* conversations can also be viewed by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Sessions --> Looking for Help`."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan *Mencari bantuan* juga dapat dilihat dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Aplikasi Live Chat --> Sesi --> Mencari Bantuan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/expertise.rst:112
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:79
msgid ""
"To join a conversation in progress, click the :icon:`fa-sign-"
"in` :guilabel:`(sign in)` icon at the top of the information panel. Doing so "
"moves the conversation back to the channel heading and reverts the status to "
"*In progress*. The customer is also informed that a new user has joined the "
"chat."
msgstr ""
"Untuk bergabung dengan percakapan yang sedang berlangsung, klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-sign-in` :guilabel:`sign in` di bagian atas panel informasi. "
"Tindakan ini memindahkan percakapan kembali ke heading channel dan "
"mengembalikan status ke *In progress*. Pelanggan juga diberitahu bahwa user "
"baru telah bergabung dalam chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:3
msgid "Information panel"
msgstr "Panel informasi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:5
msgid ""
"The **Live Chat** information panel provides agents with the context they "
"need to handle live chat conversations efficiently. It gathers key "
"information about the visitor and the conversation history, allowing agents "
"to respond faster and avoid repetitive messaging."
msgstr ""
"Panel informasi **Live Chat** memberikan agen konteks yang mereka butuhkan "
"untuk menangani percakapan live chat secara efisien. Panel ini mengumpulkan "
"informasi kunci tentang pengunjung dan riwayat percakapan, memungkinkan agen "
"merespons lebih cepat dan menghindari pesan berulang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:10
msgid "Accessing the info panel"
msgstr "Mengakses panel info"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:12
msgid ""
"To view the info panel, open a live chat conversation either in the "
"**Discuss** app or the **Live Chat** app. Live chat discussions in the "
"**Discuss** app are listed on the left side panel, under the title of the "
"live chat channel where the conversation began. In the **Live Chat** app, "
"conversations can be accessed by navigating to :menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Sessions --> All Conversations`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat panel info, buka percakapan live chat di aplikasi **Diskusi** "
"atau aplikasi **Live Chat**. Diskusi live chat di aplikasi **Diskusi** "
"terdaftar di panel sisi kiri, di bawah judul saluran live chat tempat "
"percakapan dimulai. Di aplikasi **Live Chat**, percakapan dapat diakses "
"dengan menavigasi ke :menuselection:`Live Chat --> Sesi --> Semua "
"Percakapan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:18
msgid ""
"The information panel appears on the right side of the conversation. Click "
"the :icon:`fa-info` :guilabel:`(information)` icon to toggle the info panel "
"open or closed."
msgstr ""
"Panel informasi muncul di sisi kanan percakapan. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-info` "
":guilabel:`informasi` untuk membuka atau menutup panel info."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The information panel for a known contact."
msgstr "Panel informasi untuk kontak yang dikenal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:25
msgid "Contact information"
msgstr "Informasi kontak"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:27
msgid ""
"If the live chat conversation involves a known contact, a :guilabel:`View "
"Contact` button appears at the top of the panel. Clicking this button opens "
"the :doc:`contact record <../../essentials/contacts>` for the customer, "
"without closing the conversation. The contact record links to the customers' "
"sales, invoices, meetings, and previous live chat sessions."
msgstr ""
"Jika percakapan live chat melibatkan kontak yang dikenal, tombol "
":guilabel:`Lihat Kontak` muncul di bagian atas panel. Mengklik tombol ini "
"membuka :doc:`catatan kontak <../../essentials/contacts>` untuk pelanggan, "
"tanpa menutup percakapan. Catatan kontak terhubung ke penjualan pelanggan, "
"faktur, pertemuan, dan sesi live chat sebelumnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:35
msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:37
msgid ""
"In an active livechat conversation, the *Status* can be set to allow agents "
"to identify conversations that require immediate action, and inform other "
"agents which conversations require their expertise at any given time."
msgstr ""
"Dalam percakapan livechat aktif, *Status* dapat diatur untuk memungkinkan "
"agen mengidentifikasi percakapan yang memerlukan tindakan segera, dan "
"menginformasikan agen lain percakapan mana yang memerlukan keahlian mereka "
"pada waktu tertentu."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:42
msgid "In progress"
msgstr "Dalam proses"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:44
msgid ""
"The *In progress* status is the default status for a conversation. This "
"status indicates that the customer is waiting for a response from an agent."
msgstr ""
"Status *Sedang berlangsung* adalah status default untuk percakapan. Status "
"ini menunjukkan bahwa pelanggan sedang menunggu respons dari agen."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:48
msgid ""
"If a conversation is set to *Waiting for customer*, it will revert to *In "
"progress* as soon as the customer sends a new message."
msgstr ""
"Jika percakapan diatur ke *Menunggu pelanggan*, percakapan akan kembali ke "
"*Sedang berlangsung* segera setelah pelanggan mengirim pesan baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:52
msgid "Waiting for customer"
msgstr "Menunggu pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:54
msgid ""
"The *Waiting for customer* status indicates that an agent has sent a message "
"to the customer and is waiting for a response. When this status is applied, "
"the conversation is highlighted in yellow with a :icon:`fa-hourglass-"
"start` :guilabel:`(hourglass)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Status *Menunggu pelanggan* menunjukkan bahwa agen telah mengirim pesan ke "
"pelanggan dan sedang menunggu respons. Ketika status ini diterapkan, "
"percakapan disorot dengan warna kuning dengan ikon :icon:`fa-hourglass-"
"start` :guilabel:`jam pasir`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "A conversation with the waiting for customer status."
msgstr "Percakapan dengan status menunggu pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:62
msgid "The *Waiting for customer* status **must** be manually applied."
msgstr "Status *Menunggu pelanggan* **harus** diterapkan secara manual."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:65
msgid "Looking for help"
msgstr "Mencari bantuan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:67
msgid ""
"If a conversation is marked with the status *Looking for help*, it moves "
"from its original channel name heading to the *Looking for help* heading, "
"and the :icon:`fa-exclamation-circle` :guilabel:`(exclamation circle)` icon "
"is added. Any user with **Live Chat** permissions can view or join these "
"conversations, even if they are not currently active in a live chat channel."
msgstr ""
"Jika percakapan ditandai dengan status *Mencari bantuan*, percakapan "
"berpindah dari judul nama saluran aslinya ke judul *Mencari bantuan*, dan "
"ikon :icon:`fa-exclamation-circle` :guilabel:`lingkaran seru` ditambahkan. "
"Setiap user dengan izin **Live Chat** dapat melihat atau bergabung dalam "
"percakapan ini, meskipun mereka saat ini tidak aktif dalam saluran live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:72
msgid ""
"If a conversation with the *Looking for help* status has an :ref:`expertise "
"<information/expertise>` listed that matches the user's, the conversation is "
"marked with a :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`(star)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Jika percakapan dengan status *Mencari bantuan* memiliki :ref:`keahlian "
"<information/expertise>` yang terdaftar yang cocok dengan user, percakapan "
"ditandai dengan ikon :icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`bintang`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid ""
"The looking for help panel with a star marking conversations relevant to "
"user expertise."
msgstr ""
"Panel mencari bantuan dengan tanda bintang yang menandai percakapan yang "
"relevan dengan keahlian user."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:84
msgid ""
"If the icon does not appear, manually set the status to *In progress* to "
"inform other agents the conversation is being handled."
msgstr ""
"Jika ikon tidak muncul, atur status secara manual ke *In progress* untuk "
"memberi tahu agen lain bahwa percakapan sedang ditangani."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:88
msgid ""
"All conversations that have been tagged with the status *Looking for help* "
"can be found by navigating to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Sessions --> "
"Looking for Help`. Use the filters to find the appropriate session date."
msgstr ""
"Semua percakapan yang telah ditandai dengan status *Looking for help* dapat "
"ditemukan dengan membuka :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Sessions --> "
"Looking for Help`. Gunakan filter untuk menemukan tanggal sesi yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:93
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Catatan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:95
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Notes` field allows agents to leave comments about the "
"conversation, recap the situation when transferring it to another agent, or  "
"to add context to the conversation that can be viewed later in reporting."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Notes` memungkinkan agen untuk meninggalkan komentar "
"tentang percakapan, merangkum situasi saat mentransfer ke agen lain, atau "
"menambahkan konteks ke percakapan yang dapat dilihat kemudian dalam "
"pelaporan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:102
msgid ""
"Tags can be added to a conversation to assist with categorizing, tracking "
"issues, and enhancing reporting. Click :guilabel:`Tags` :icon:`fa-plus`, "
"then select a tag from the list, or enter a new one in the field. Multiple "
"tags can be added to a single conversation."
msgstr ""
"Tag dapat ditambahkan ke percakapan untuk membantu kategorisasi, pelacakan "
"masalah, dan meningkatkan pelaporan. Klik :guilabel:`Tags` :icon:`fa-plus`, "
"kemudian pilih tag dari daftar, atau masukkan tag baru di kolom. Beberapa "
"tag dapat ditambahkan ke satu percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:107
msgid "Chatbot answers"
msgstr "Jawaban-jawaban chatbot"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the conversation was forwarded from a chatbot, the answers selected from "
"the chatbot are included on the information panel under *Chatbot answers*."
msgstr ""
"Jika percakapan diteruskan dari chatbot, jawaban yang dipilih dari chatbot "
"disertakan di panel informasi di bawah *Chatbot answers*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The chatbot answers section of the information panel."
msgstr "Bagian chatbot answers pada panel informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Expertise` field allows agents to designate the topic of "
"conversation to a specific skillset or knowledge scope. This helps to "
"categorize the conversation for assignment purposes, as well as issue "
"tacking and enchanced reporting. Click into the field and select one or more "
"options from the drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Kolom :guilabel:`Expertise` memungkinkan agen untuk menentukan topik "
"percakapan ke keahlian atau cakupan pengetahuan tertentu. Ini membantu "
"mengkategorikan percakapan untuk tujuan penugasan, serta pelacakan masalah "
"dan pelaporan yang lebih baik. Klik ke dalam kolom dan pilih satu atau lebih "
"opsi dari daftar drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:126
msgid "Country & language"
msgstr "Negara & bahasa"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:128
msgid ""
"The *Country & Language* section identifies where the customer is located, "
"and their language. A visitor's language is determined via their browser's "
"language settings."
msgstr ""
"Bagian *Country & Language* mengidentifikasi lokasi pelanggan dan bahasa "
"mereka. Bahasa pengunjung ditentukan melalui pengaturan bahasa browser "
"mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:132
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:39
msgid ""
"Conversations are assigned to operators based on a number of criteria, "
"including availability and the number of ongoing conversations. While the "
"operator's main language and additional languages are taken into "
"consideration, they do **not** supersede all other criteria."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan ditetapkan kepada operator berdasarkan sejumlah kriteria, "
"termasuk ketersediaan dan jumlah percakapan yang sedang berlangsung. "
"Meskipun bahasa utama operator dan bahasa tambahan dipertimbangkan, mereka "
"**tidak** menggantikan semua kriteria lainnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:137
msgid "Recent conversations"
msgstr "Percakapan-percakapan terkini"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:139
msgid ""
"Any recent live chat conversations with this customer also appear in the "
"information panel. Click on the :icon:`fa-external-"
"link` :guilabel:`(external link)` icon on the ticket title to open the "
"conversation in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan live chat terkini dengan pelanggan ini juga muncul di panel "
"informasi. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-external-link` :guilabel:`external link` pada "
"judul tiket untuk membuka percakapan di tab baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The recent conversations field on the information panel."
msgstr "Kolom recent conversations pada panel informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:147
msgid "Open tickets"
msgstr "Buka tiket-tiket"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:149
msgid ""
"Any open **Helpdesk** tickets created by the customer also appear in the "
"information panel. Click on the :icon:`fa-external-"
"link` :guilabel:`(external link)` icon on the ticket title to open the "
"ticket record in a new tab."
msgstr ""
"Tiket **Pusat Bantuan** yang terbuka yang dibuat oleh pelanggan juga muncul "
"di panel informasi. Klik ikon :icon:`fa-external-link` :guilabel:`external "
"link` pada judul tiket untuk membuka catatan tiket di tab baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The open ticket field on the information panel."
msgstr "Kolom open ticket pada panel informasi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:157
msgid "Outcome"
msgstr "Hasil"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:159
msgid ""
"For closed conversations, the *Outcome* field defines how the conversation "
"concluded:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk percakapan yang ditutup, kolom *Outcome* menentukan bagaimana "
"percakapan berakhir:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:161
msgid ""
"*No Answer*: assigned when the customer does not respond to the agent. This "
"usually occurs when the session is initiated, but the customer does not "
"engage or send additional messages."
msgstr ""
"*No Answer*: ditetapkan ketika pelanggan tidak merespons agen. Ini biasanya "
"terjadi ketika sesi dimulai, tetapi pelanggan tidak terlibat atau mengirim "
"pesan tambahan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:163
msgid ""
"*No One Available*: assigned when no agents are available to respond to the "
"customer. This occurs when the session is initiated, but no operator is "
"online or available to be assigned to the chat."
msgstr ""
"*No One Available*: ditetapkan ketika tidak ada agen yang tersedia untuk "
"merespons pelanggan. Ini terjadi ketika sesi dimulai, tetapi tidak ada "
"operator yang online atau tersedia untuk ditugaskan ke chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:165
msgid ""
"*Success*: assigned when the live chat session is completed successfully. "
"This outcome does **not** depend the customer providing a positive rating, "
"it is dependent on the session being resolved without escalation or failure."
msgstr ""
"*Success*: ditetapkan ketika sesi live chat selesai dengan sukses. Hasil ini "
"**tidak** bergantung pada pelanggan memberikan rating positif, tetapi "
"bergantung pada sesi yang diselesaikan tanpa eskalasi atau kegagalan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:168
msgid ""
"*Escalated*: assigned when the session is forwarded to another operator. "
"This indicates the initial operator could not resolve the issue, and "
"required assistance."
msgstr ""
"*Escalated*: ditetapkan ketika sesi diteruskan ke operator lain. Ini "
"menunjukkan bahwa operator awal tidak dapat menyelesaikan masalah dan "
"memerlukan bantuan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:172
msgid "Send conversation"
msgstr "Kirim percakapan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:174
msgid ""
"When the conversation is complete, scroll to the bottom of the info panel. "
"The email address in the field can be edited to send to a different "
"address.click the :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(paper plane)` icon to "
"send a copy of the conversation transcript."
msgstr ""
"Ketika percakapan selesai, gulir ke bagian bawah panel info. Alamat email di "
"kolom dapat diedit untuk mengirim ke alamat yang berbeda. klik ikon "
":icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(pesawat kertas)` untuk mengirim salinan "
"transkrip percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/information.rst:None
msgid "The send conversation button at the bottom of the info panel."
msgstr "Tombol kirim percakapan di bagian bawah panel info."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:3
msgid "Participate in live chat"
msgstr "Berpartisipasi dalam live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:5
msgid ""
"*Operators* are the users who respond to live chat requests from customers "
"and website visitors. The information below outlines the necessary steps for "
"operators participating in live chat conversations on an Odoo database."
msgstr ""
"*Operator* adalah user yang merespons permintaan live chat dari pelanggan "
"dan pengunjung website. Informasi di bawah ini menguraikan langkah-langkah "
"yang diperlukan bagi operator yang berpartisipasi dalam percakapan live chat "
"di database Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:10
msgid "Set an online chat name"
msgstr "Mengatur nama chat online"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:12
msgid ""
"Before participating in a live chat, operators may choose to update their "
"*Online Chat Name*. This is the name displayed to site visitors in the live "
"chat conversation."
msgstr ""
"Sebelum berpartisipasi dalam live chat, operator dapat memilih untuk "
"memperbarui *Nama Chat Online* mereka. Ini adalah nama yang ditampilkan "
"kepada pengunjung situs dalam percakapan live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:15
msgid ""
"To update the *Online Chat Name*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, locate the :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` "
"field, and enter a preferred name."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memperbarui *Nama Chat Online*, klik avatar user di sudut kanan atas "
"halaman mana pun di database. Pilih :guilabel:`My Profile` dari menu drop-"
"down untuk membuka halaman profil. Di sisi kanan tab "
":guilabel:`Preferences`, temukan bidang :guilabel:`Online Chat Name`, dan "
"masukkan nama yang diinginkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:20
msgid ""
"If a user's :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` is not set, the name displayed "
"defaults to the user's name that is designated on their profile page."
msgstr ""
"Jika :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` user tidak diatur, nama yang ditampilkan "
"default menjadi nama user yang ditetapkan di halaman profil mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:24
msgid ""
"A user has their full name as their :guilabel:`User Name`, but they do not "
"want to include their last name in a live chat conversation. They would then "
"set their :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` to include only their first name."
msgstr ""
"Seorang user memiliki nama lengkap sebagai :guilabel:`User Name` mereka, "
"tetapi mereka tidak ingin menyertakan nama belakang mereka dalam percakapan "
"live chat. Mereka kemudian akan mengatur :guilabel:`Online Chat Name` mereka "
"untuk hanya menyertakan nama depan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of user profile in Odoo, emphasizing the Online Chat name field."
msgstr "Tampilan profil user di Odoo, yang menekankan bidang Online Chat name."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:32
msgid "Set online chat languages"
msgstr "Mengatur bahasa chat online"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:34
msgid ""
"If an operator speaks multiple languages, they can add this information to "
"their user profile. This information can then be used to determine which "
"conversations the operator is assigned. A visitor's language is determined "
"via their browser's language settings."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator berbicara dalam beberapa bahasa, mereka dapat menambahkan "
"informasi ini ke profil user mereka. Informasi ini kemudian dapat digunakan "
"untuk menentukan percakapan mana yang ditetapkan kepada operator. Bahasa "
"pengunjung ditentukan melalui pengaturan bahasa browser mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:43
msgid ""
"To add *Online Chat Languages*, click on the user avatar in the top-right "
"corner of any page in the database. Select :guilabel:`My Profile` from the "
"drop-down menu to open the profile page. On the right side of "
"the :guilabel:`Preferences` tab, click into the :guilabel:`Online Chat "
"Language` field, and select one or more languages from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan *Bahasa Chat Online*, klik avatar user di sudut kanan atas "
"halaman mana pun di database. Pilih :guilabel:`My Profile` dari menu drop-"
"down untuk membuka halaman profil. Di sisi kanan tab "
":guilabel:`Preferences`, klik ke dalam bidang :guilabel:`Online Chat "
"Language`, dan pilih satu atau lebih bahasa dari menu drop-down."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:49
msgid ""
"Only :doc:`languages <../../general/users/language>` that are enabled on the "
"database can be selected in the :guilabel:`Online Chat Language` field."
msgstr ""
"Hanya :doc:`bahasa <../../general/users/language>` yang diaktifkan di "
"database yang dapat dipilih di bidang :guilabel:`Online Chat Language`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:55
msgid ""
"Operators can designate *Expertise* in one or more areas on their profile. "
"A :doc:`chatbot <chatbots>` can then assign conversations to the operator "
"with the appropriate expertise. Select one or more options from "
"the :guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Operator dapat menetapkan *Keahlian* dalam satu atau lebih area di profil "
"mereka. :doc:`Chatbot <chatbots>` kemudian dapat menetapkan percakapan "
"kepada operator dengan keahlian yang sesuai. Pilih satu atau lebih opsi dari "
"daftar drop-down :guilabel:`Live Chat Expertise`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:59
msgid ""
"To create a new expertise, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Expertise` and click :guilabel:`New`. Enter "
"the :guilabel:`Name` of the expertise, and, if desired, select one or "
"more :guilabel:`Operators`. Click :guilabel:`Save` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat keahlian baru, buka :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Expertise` dan klik :guilabel:`New`. Masukkan "
":guilabel:`Name` dari keahlian tersebut, dan, jika diinginkan, pilih satu "
"atau lebih :guilabel:`Operators`. Klik :guilabel:`Save` setelah selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:64
msgid ""
"When forwarding live chat conversations, the chatbot prioritizes users with "
"matching expertise. If no applicable match is found, the chatbot forwards "
"the conversation to the next available operator."
msgstr ""
"Ketika meneruskan percakapan live chat, chatbot memprioritaskan user dengan "
"keahlian yang sesuai. Jika tidak ditemukan kecocokan yang sesuai, chatbot "
"meneruskan percakapan ke operator yang tersedia berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:69
msgid "Join or leave a channel"
msgstr "Bergabung atau meninggalkan channel"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:71
msgid ""
"To join a live chat channel, go to the :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Channels`, and click the :guilabel:`Join` button on the Kanban card for the "
"appropriate channel."
msgstr ""
"Untuk bergabung dengan channel live chat, buka :menuselection:`Live Chat "
"app --> Channels`, dan klik tombol :guilabel:`Join` pada kartu Kanban untuk "
"channel yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:74
msgid ""
"Any channel where the user is currently active shows a :guilabel:`Leave` "
"button. Click this button to disconnect from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Setiap channel di mana user sedang aktif menampilkan tombol "
":guilabel:`Leave`. Klik tombol ini untuk terputus dari channel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a channel form and the option to join a channel for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan formulir channel dan opsi untuk bergabung dengan channel untuk Odoo "
"Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:81
msgid ""
"Operators that do not show any activity in Odoo for more than thirty minutes "
"are considered disconnected, and subsequently removed from the channel."
msgstr ""
"Operator yang tidak menunjukkan aktivitas apa pun di Odoo selama lebih dari "
"tiga puluh menit dianggap terputus, dan kemudian dihapus dari channel."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:85
msgid "Manage live chat requests"
msgstr "Mengelola permintaan live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:87
msgid ""
"When an operator is active in a channel, chat windows open in the bottom-"
"right corner of the screen, no matter where they are in the database. This "
"allows them to access other pages and apps, while still participating in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Ketika operator aktif dalam sebuah channel, jendela chat terbuka di sudut "
"kanan bawah layar, di mana pun mereka berada dalam database. Hal ini "
"memungkinkan mereka untuk mengakses halaman dan app lain, sambil tetap "
"berpartisipasi dalam percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:91
msgid ""
"Live chat conversations can also be viewed by navigating to "
"the :menuselection:`Discuss app`. New conversations appear in bold under the "
"channel name, located along the left panel."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan live chat juga dapat dilihat dengan membuka "
":menuselection:`Discuss app`. Percakapan baru muncul dalam huruf tebal di "
"bawah nama channel, yang terletak di panel kiri."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the discuss application with a message sent through live chat in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan aplikasi Diskusi dengan pesan yang dikirim melalui live chat di "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click on a conversation in the left panel to select it. This opens the "
"conversation. From this view, an operator can participate in the chat the "
"same as they would in the normal chat window."
msgstr ""
"Klik percakapan di panel kiri untuk memilihnya. Ini akan membuka percakapan. "
"Dari tampilan ini, operator dapat berpartisipasi dalam chat sama seperti di "
"jendela chat normal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:101
msgid ""
"Conversations can also be accessed by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"comments` :guilabel:`(Messages)` icon in the menu bar."
msgstr ""
"Percakapan juga dapat diakses dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`fa-comments` "
":guilabel:`(Messages)` di menu bar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:0
msgid "View of the menu bar in Odoo emphasizing the comments icon."
msgstr "Tampilan menu bar di Odoo yang menekankan ikon komentar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:108
msgid ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:109
msgid ":doc:`../livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/participate.rst:110
msgid ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`../livechat/responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:3
msgid "Ratings"
msgstr "Rating"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:9
msgid ""
"At the end of a **Live Chat** conversation, customers have the opportunity "
"to rate the quality of support they received from the live chat *operator*. "
"Customers provide ratings as soon as they close the conversation. This "
"allows operators to receive immediate feedback on their performance. It also "
"allows customers to share any final comments before leaving the chat window."
msgstr ""
"Di akhir percakapan **Live Chat**, pelanggan memiliki kesempatan untuk "
"menilai kualitas dukungan yang mereka terima dari *operator* live chat. "
"Pelanggan memberikan penilaian segera setelah mereka menutup percakapan. Hal "
"ini memungkinkan operator untuk menerima umpan balik langsung tentang "
"kinerja mereka. Ini juga memungkinkan pelanggan untuk berbagi komentar "
"terakhir sebelum meninggalkan jendela chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:15
msgid "Rate live chat conversations"
msgstr "Menilai percakapan live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:17
msgid ""
"Customers end a live chat conversation by clicking the :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(close)` icon in the upper right-hand corner of the chat "
"window. They are then prompted to select an icon that reflects their level "
"of satisfaction. The icons represent the following ratings:"
msgstr ""
"Pelanggan mengakhiri percakapan live chat dengan mengklik ikon :icon:`oi-"
"close` :guilabel:`(close)` di sudut kanan atas jendela chat. Mereka kemudian "
"diminta untuk memilih ikon yang mencerminkan tingkat kepuasan mereka. Ikon-"
"ikon tersebut mewakili penilaian berikut:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:21
msgid "**Satisfied** - |smile|"
msgstr "**Puas** - |smile|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:22
msgid "**Okay** - |meh|"
msgstr "**Cukup** - |meh|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:23
msgid "**Dissatisfied** - |frown|"
msgstr "**Tidak Puas** - |frown|"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat window from a user's side for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan jendela obrolan dari sisi user untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:29
msgid ""
"When customers end a conversation, a field marked :guilabel:`Receive a copy "
"of this conversation` appears under the *ratings* icons. Customers can enter "
"their email either before or after they submit a rating."
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan mengakhiri percakapan, bidang yang bertanda "
":guilabel:`Terima salinan percakapan ini` muncul di bawah ikon *peringkat*. "
"Pelanggan dapat memasukkan email mereka sebelum atau setelah mereka "
"mengirimkan peringkat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:33
msgid ""
"If the customer selects the |smile|, they are presented with a thank you "
"message and a :guilabel:`Close Conversation` link."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan memilih |smile|, mereka akan disajikan pesan terima kasih dan "
"tautan :guilabel:`Tutup Percakapan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of customer's live chat window with thank you message."
msgstr "Tampilan jendela live chat pelanggan dengan pesan terima kasih."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:39
msgid ""
"If the customer selects either the |meh| or the |frown|, a text box appears. "
"Customers can add comments in this text box to explain why they chose this "
"rating. This message, along with the rating icon, is sent to the live chat "
"operator."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan memilih |meh| atau |frown|, kotak teks muncul. Pelanggan "
"dapat menambahkan komentar di kotak teks ini untuk menjelaskan mengapa "
"mereka memilih peringkat ini. Pesan ini, bersama dengan ikon peringkat, "
"dikirim ke operator live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of a chat window from an operator's window highlighting a rating for "
"Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan jendela obrolan dari jendela operator yang menyorot peringkat untuk "
"Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:47
msgid "Publish customer ratings"
msgstr "Publikasikan peringkat pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:49
msgid ""
"To publish a channel's ratings on the website, first navigate to a live chat "
"channel's record by going to the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and clicking "
"on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the "
"Kanban card for that team. Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open "
"the channel details form. Then click on the :guilabel:`Go to Website` smart "
"button. This opens the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channel Statistics` page."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mempublikasikan peringkat channel di website, pertama navigasikan ke "
"record channel live chat dengan membuka aplikasi :menuselection:`Live Chat` "
"dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`elipsis vertikal` pada kartu "
"Kanban untuk tim tersebut. Kemudian, klik :guilabel:`Konfigurasi Channel` "
"untuk membuka formulir detail channel. Kemudian klik tombol pintar "
":guilabel:`Buka Website`. Ini membuka halaman :guilabel:`Statistik Channel "
"Live Chat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:55
msgid ""
"In the upper right corner of the page, click the red :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"slider. The slider changes from :guilabel:`Unpublished` "
"to :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Di sudut kanan atas halaman, klik slider merah :guilabel:`Belum "
"Dipublikasikan`. Slider berubah dari :guilabel:`Belum Dipublikasikan` "
"menjadi :guilabel:`Dipublikasikan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the published ratings on the portal for Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan peringkat yang dipublikasikan di portal untuk Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:62
msgid ""
"The customer notes submitted with the rating are *not* published on the "
"website; they are kept internal. Only a statistical overview of the "
"operators' performance for the *channel* appears on the website."
msgstr ""
"Catatan pelanggan yang dikirimkan bersama peringkat *tidak* dipublikasikan "
"di website; catatan tersebut disimpan secara internal. Hanya tinjauan "
"statistik kinerja operator untuk *channel* yang muncul di website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:67
msgid "Add ratings page to site"
msgstr "Tambahkan halaman peringkat ke situs"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:69
msgid ""
"Once the rating page has been published, it has to be manually added to the "
"website. To do this, go to the main Odoo dashboard and open the **Website** "
"application. :menuselection:`Website app --> Site --> Pages`, then "
"click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah halaman peringkat dipublikasikan, halaman tersebut harus ditambahkan "
"secara manual ke website. Untuk melakukan ini, buka Dashboard Odoo utama dan "
"buka aplikasi **Website**. :menuselection:`Aplikasi Website --> Situs --> "
"Halaman`, kemudian klik :guilabel:`Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:73
msgid ""
"This opens a :guilabel:`New Page` pop-up window. In the :guilabel:`Page "
"Title` field, enter `livechat`. This acts as the URL for the published "
"webpage."
msgstr ""
"Ini membuka jendela pop-up :guilabel:`Halaman Baru`. Di bidang "
":guilabel:`Judul Halaman`, masukkan `livechat`. Ini berfungsi sebagai URL "
"untuk halaman web yang dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:77
msgid ""
"The URL *must* be named `livechat` in order for the database to recognize "
"and connect the ratings page. After the page has been published, the page "
"title can be changed later under the :guilabel:`Menu Editor`."
msgstr ""
"URL *harus* diberi nama `livechat` agar database mengenali dan menghubungkan "
"halaman peringkat. Setelah halaman dipublikasikan, judul halaman dapat "
"diubah nanti di bawah :guilabel:`Editor Menu`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Create`, and the newly created webpage opens. "
"The :guilabel:`Web Editor` appears in the right panel."
msgstr ""
"Klik :guilabel:`Buat`, dan halaman web yang baru dibuat terbuka. "
":guilabel:`Editor Web` muncul di panel kanan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:84
msgid ""
"The page lists the names of the :guilabel:`Live Chat Channels` whose ratings "
"pages have been published. On the left side of the channel name is an icon, "
"which users can click on to go to the ratings page for the respective "
"channel."
msgstr ""
"Halaman mencantumkan nama-nama :guilabel:`Channel Live Chat` yang halaman "
"peringkatnya telah dipublikasikan. Di sisi kiri nama channel terdapat ikon, "
"yang dapat diklik pengguna untuk membuka halaman peringkat untuk channel "
"masing-masing."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the webpage for Live Chat ratings emphasizing the channel icon."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan halaman web untuk penilaian Live Chat yang menekankan ikon saluran."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:92
msgid ""
"The icon displayed on this page is configured on the live chat channel's "
"configuration page. To update this image, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Live Chat` app and click on the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon on the Kanban card for that team. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Configure Channel` to open the channel details form. "
"Click the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pencil)` icon in the image box to "
"upload an image."
msgstr ""
"Ikon yang ditampilkan di halaman ini dikonfigurasi pada halaman konfigurasi "
"saluran live chat. Untuk memperbarui gambar ini, navigasi ke aplikasi "
":menuselection:`Live Chat` dan klik ikon :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`"
"(ellipsis vertikal)` pada kartu Kanban untuk tim tersebut. Kemudian, klik "
":guilabel:`Configure Channel` untuk membuka formulir detail saluran. Klik "
"ikon :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(pensil)` di kotak gambar untuk mengunggah "
"gambar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:98
msgid ""
"Make any desired changes or additions to this page, then "
"click :guilabel:`Save` in the top right of the webpage editor. The website "
"editor side panel closes, and the webpage remains on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Buat perubahan atau penambahan yang diinginkan pada halaman ini, lalu klik "
":guilabel:`Save` di kanan atas editor halaman web. Panel samping editor "
"website menutup, dan halaman web tetap di layar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:101
msgid ""
"To publish the `livechat` webpage, return to the list of webpages by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Site --> Content --> Pages`. Click the "
"checkbox to the left of `livechat` in the list of pages to select the page "
"and highlight the line. Then, click the checkbox under the column "
"labeled :guilabel:`Is Published`. The field with the checkbox is highlighted "
"in white. Click the checkbox a second time to activate the :guilabel:`Is "
"Published` box. The webpage is now published."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mempublikasikan halaman web `livechat`, kembali ke daftar halaman web "
"dengan navigasi ke :menuselection:`Site --> Content --> Pages`. Klik kotak "
"centang di sebelah kiri `livechat` dalam daftar halaman untuk memilih "
"halaman dan menyorot baris. Kemudian, klik kotak centang di bawah kolom "
"berlabel :guilabel:`Is Published`. Bidang dengan kotak centang disorot "
"dengan warna putih. Klik kotak centang untuk kedua kalinya untuk "
"mengaktifkan kotak :guilabel:`Is Published`. Halaman web sekarang "
"dipublikasikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the list of pages for a website with the 'is published' box "
"emphasized."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan daftar halaman untuk website dengan kotak 'is published' yang "
"ditekankan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:110
msgid ""
"Once the page has been added to the site, ratings are set to be published by "
"default. However, individual ratings can be manually selected to be hidden "
"from the public. The rating is still included in internal reports, and can "
"still be viewed by internal teams. However, public website visitors and "
"portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Setelah halaman ditambahkan ke situs, penilaian diatur untuk dipublikasikan "
"secara default. Namun, penilaian individual dapat dipilih secara manual "
"untuk disembunyikan dari publik. Penilaian tersebut masih termasuk dalam "
"laporan internal, dan masih dapat dilihat oleh tim internal. Namun, "
"pengunjung website publik dan pengguna portal tidak memiliki akses."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:115
msgid ""
"See :ref:`Hide individual ratings <livechat/overview/hide-ratings>` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Lihat :ref:`Hide individual ratings <livechat/overview/hide-ratings>` untuk "
"informasi lebih lanjut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:118
msgid "Customer ratings report"
msgstr "Laporan penilaian pelanggan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:120
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer Ratings` report (:menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Report --> Customer Ratings`) displays an overview of the ratings received "
"on live chat conversations, as well as any additional comments submitted "
"with the rating."
msgstr ""
"Laporan :guilabel:`Customer Ratings` (:menuselection:`Live Chat --> "
"Report --> Customer Ratings`) menampilkan gambaran umum penilaian yang "
"diterima pada percakapan live chat, serta komentar tambahan yang dikirimkan "
"bersama penilaian."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid "View of the customer ratings report in Odoo Live Chat."
msgstr "Tampilan laporan penilaian pelanggan di Odoo Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:127
msgid ""
"The report defaults to a Kanban view, with each rating represented by a "
"different card. To switch to a different view, click on one of the icons in "
"the upper-right corner of the screen. The report is available in *list* "
"view, *pivot* view, and *graph* view."
msgstr ""
"Laporan default ke tampilan Kanban, dengan setiap penilaian diwakili oleh "
"kartu yang berbeda. Untuk beralih ke tampilan lain, klik salah satu ikon di "
"sudut kanan atas layar. Laporan tersedia dalam tampilan *list*, tampilan "
"*pivot*, dan tampilan *graph*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:131
msgid ""
"Click on an individual rating to see additional details about the "
"conversation, and the rating."
msgstr ""
"Klik pada penilaian individual untuk melihat detail tambahan tentang "
"percakapan, dan penilaian."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:136
msgid "Hide individual ratings"
msgstr "Sembunyikan penilaian individual"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:138
msgid ""
"Ratings are set to be published by default. However, individual ratings can "
"be manually selected to be hidden from the public. The rating is still "
"included in internal reports, and can still be viewed by internal teams. "
"However, public website visitors and portal users do not have access."
msgstr ""
"Penilaian diatur untuk dipublikasikan secara default. Namun, penilaian "
"individual dapat dipilih secara manual untuk disembunyikan dari publik. "
"Penilaian tersebut masih termasuk dalam laporan internal, dan masih dapat "
"dilihat oleh tim internal. Namun, pengunjung website publik dan pengguna "
"portal tidak memiliki akses."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:142
msgid ""
"To hide a rating, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report --> "
"Customer Ratings`. Click on the Kanban card for the rating to be hidden. On "
"the individual rating's detail page, check the box "
"labeled :guilabel:`Visible Internally Only`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyembunyikan penilaian, buka :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Report --> Customer Ratings`. Klik pada kartu Kanban untuk penilaian yang "
"akan disembunyikan. Pada halaman detail penilaian individual, centang kotak "
"berlabel :guilabel:`Visible Internally Only`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of an individual rating's detail page with the visible internally "
"setting checked."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan halaman detail penilaian individual dengan pengaturan visible "
"internally yang dicentang."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:150
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/livechat`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:151
msgid ":doc:`responses`"
msgstr ":doc:`responses`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/ratings.rst:152
msgid ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/websites/website`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:3
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** includes several reports that allow for the monitoring of "
"operator performance and the identification of trends in customer "
"conversations."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Live Chat** mencakup beberapa laporan yang memungkinkan pemantauan "
"kinerja operator dan identifikasi tren dalam percakapan pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:8
msgid "The following reports are included in the **Live Chat** app:"
msgstr "Laporan berikut disertakan dalam aplikasi **Live Chat**:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:10
msgid ":ref:`Sessions History <livechat/sessions-history>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Riwayat Sesi <livechat/sessions-history>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:11
msgid ":ref:`Session Statistics <livechat/session-statistics>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Statistik Sesi <livechat/session-statistics>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:12
msgid ":ref:`Operator Analysis <livechat/operator-analysis>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Analisis Operator <livechat/operator-analysis>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:15
msgid ""
"The *Live Chat Ratings Report* can also be accessed through "
"the :guilabel:`Report` menu. For more information on this report, and on the "
"**Live Chat** rating process, see :doc:`Live Chat Ratings <../livechat/"
"ratings>`."
msgstr ""
"*Laporan Penilaian Live Chat* juga dapat diakses melalui menu "
":guilabel:`Laporan`. Untuk informasi lebih lanjut tentang laporan ini dan "
"proses penilaian **Live Chat**, lihat :doc:`Penilaian Live Chat <../livechat/"
"ratings>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:19
msgid ""
"To access a drop-down menu of all the available reports, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses menu tarik-turun dari semua laporan yang tersedia, navigasi "
"ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Live Chat --> Laporan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:25
msgid "Sessions History"
msgstr "Sejarah Sesi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:27
msgid ""
"The *Sessions History* report displays an overview of live chat sessions, "
"including session dates, participant name and country, session duration, the "
"number of messages, and the rating. It also provides access to the complete "
"transcripts of live chat sessions."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *Riwayat Sesi* menampilkan ringkasan sesi live chat, termasuk "
"tanggal sesi, nama dan negara peserta, durasi sesi, jumlah pesan, dan "
"penilaian. Laporan ini juga menyediakan akses ke transkrip lengkap dari sesi "
"live chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:31
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Report "
"--> Sessions History`. Each live chat session is represented by a Kanban "
"card."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses laporan ini, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Live "
"Chat --> Laporan --> Riwayat Sesi`. Setiap sesi live chat diwakili oleh "
"kartu Kanban."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Sessions History report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Contoh laporan Riwayat Sesi dari aplikasi Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:37
msgid ""
"To view the transcript from a specific session, click the Kanban card. This "
"opens the *Discuss* thread for the conversation."
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat transkrip dari sesi tertentu, klik kartu Kanban. Ini akan "
"membuka thread *Diskusi* untuk percakapan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:40
msgid ""
"In the *Discuss* thread, the conversation view displays the entire "
"transcript of the conversation. If the visitor left a rating, it is included "
"at the end of the transcript."
msgstr ""
"Dalam thread *Diskusi*, tampilan percakapan menampilkan seluruh transkrip "
"percakapan. Jika pengunjung meninggalkan penilaian, penilaian tersebut "
"disertakan di akhir transkrip."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "View of the chat transcript in the Discuss application."
msgstr "Tampilan transkrip obrolan dalam aplikasi Diskusi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:47
msgid "Export sessions history"
msgstr "Ekspor riwayat sesi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:49
msgid ""
"The information in this report can be exported, or inserted into a "
"spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Informasi dalam laporan ini dapat diekspor atau disisipkan ke dalam "
"spreadsheet."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:51
msgid ""
"On the *Sessions History* report, click the :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(List)` icon to switch to list view. Next, click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(gear)` icon to the right of "
"the :guilabel:`History` page title to reveal a drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Pada laporan *Riwayat Sesi*, klik ikon :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`"
"(Daftar)` untuk beralih ke tampilan daftar. Selanjutnya, klik ikon :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(roda gigi)` di sebelah kanan judul halaman "
":guilabel:`Riwayat` untuk menampilkan menu tarik-turun."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:55
msgid ""
"From the drop-down menu, click :guilabel:`Export All` to export all sessions "
"to a spreadsheet, or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet` to insert the "
"information in a new, or existing, spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Dari menu tarik-turun, klik :guilabel:`Ekspor Semua` untuk mengekspor semua "
"sesi ke spreadsheet, atau :guilabel:`Sisipkan daftar dalam spreadsheet` "
"untuk menyisipkan informasi dalam spreadsheet baru atau yang sudah ada."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:58
msgid ""
"To only export select sessions, first select the desired sessions to be "
"exported from the list, by clicking the checkbox to the left of each "
"individual session. With the sessions selected, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon at the top of the page, and "
"click :guilabel:`Export` or :guilabel:`Insert list in spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk hanya mengekspor sesi tertentu, pertama pilih sesi yang diinginkan "
"untuk diekspor dari daftar dengan mengklik kotak centang di sebelah kiri "
"setiap sesi individual. Dengan sesi yang dipilih, klik ikon :icon:`fa-cog` "
":guilabel:`Tindakan` di bagian atas halaman, dan klik :guilabel:`Ekspor` "
"atau :guilabel:`Sisipkan daftar dalam spreadsheet`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:66
msgid "Session Statistics"
msgstr "Statistik Sesi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:68
msgid ""
"The *Session Statistics* report provides a statistical overview of live chat "
"sessions. The default view for this report displays sessions grouped by the "
"date of creation."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *Statistik Sesi* memberikan ringkasan statistik dari sesi live chat. "
"Tampilan default untuk laporan ini menampilkan sesi yang dikelompokkan "
"berdasarkan tanggal pembuatan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:71
msgid ""
"To access this report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Session Statistics`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses laporan ini, navigasi ke :menuselection:`Aplikasi Live "
"Chat --> Laporan --> Statistik Sesi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"Example of the Sessions Statistics report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Contoh laporan Statistik Sesi dari aplikasi Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:77
msgid ""
"The stacked bar graph view of the *Session Statistics* report, with results "
"grouped by Creation Date (hour), then by rating."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan grafik batang bertumpuk dari laporan *Statistik Sesi*, dengan hasil "
"dikelompokkan berdasarkan Tanggal Pembuatan (jam), kemudian berdasarkan "
"rating."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:112
msgid ""
"To view a different measure, click the :guilabel:`Measures` drop-down menu "
"at the top-left of the report. The measures available for this report "
"include:"
msgstr ""
"Untuk melihat ukuran yang berbeda, klik menu tarik-turun :guilabel:`Ukuran` "
"di kiri atas laporan. Ukuran yang tersedia untuk laporan ini meliputi:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:83
msgid ":guilabel:`# of speakers`: number of participants in the conversation."
msgstr ":guilabel:`# pembicara`: jumlah peserta dalam percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:84
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Days of activity`: number of days since the operator's first "
"session."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Hari aktif`: jumlah hari sejak sesi pertama operator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:85
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration of Session (min)`: the duration of a conversation, in "
"minutes."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Durasi Sesi (menit)`: durasi percakapan, dalam menit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:86
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is visitor anonymous`: denotes whether the conversation "
"participant is anonymous."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pengunjung anonim`: menunjukkan apakah peserta percakapan "
"bersifat anonim."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:87
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Messages per session`: the total number of messages sent in a "
"conversation. This measure is included in the default view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pesan per sesi`: jumlah total pesan yang dikirim dalam "
"percakapan. Ukuran ini disertakan dalam tampilan default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:89
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: the rating received by an operator at the end of a "
"session, if one was provided."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rating`: rating yang diterima oleh operator di akhir sesi, jika "
"diberikan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Session not rated`: denotes if a session did **not** receive a "
"rating at the end of the conversation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sesi tidak diberi rating`: menunjukkan apakah sesi **tidak** "
"menerima rating di akhir percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer (sec)`: the average time, in seconds, before an "
"operator responds to a chat request."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Waktu untuk menjawab (det)`: waktu rata-rata, dalam detik, "
"sebelum operator merespons permintaan chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:95
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visitor is Happy`: denotes whether a positive rating was "
"provided. If the visitor gave either a negative or neutral rating, they are "
"considered *unhappy*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Pengunjung Puas`: menunjukkan apakah rating positif diberikan. "
"Jika pengunjung memberikan rating negatif atau netral, mereka dianggap "
"*tidak puas*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:97
#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:121
msgid ":guilabel:`Count`: the total number of sessions."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Jumlah`: jumlah total sesi."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:102
msgid "Operator Analysis"
msgstr "Analisis Operator"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:104
msgid ""
"The *Operator Analysis* report is used to monitor the performance of "
"individual live chat operators."
msgstr ""
"Laporan *Analisis Operator* digunakan untuk memantau kinerja operator live "
"chat individual."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:106
msgid ""
"To access the report, navigate to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> Reports "
"--> Operator Analysis`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses laporan, navigasikan ke :menuselection:`aplikasi Live "
"Chat --> Laporan --> Analisis Operator`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:108
msgid ""
"The default view for this report is a bar chart, which only displays "
"conversations from the current month, as indicated by the :guilabel:`This "
"Month` default search filter. Conversations are grouped by operator."
msgstr ""
"Tampilan default untuk laporan ini adalah grafik batang, yang hanya "
"menampilkan percakapan dari bulan ini, seperti yang ditunjukkan oleh filter "
"pencarian default :guilabel:`Bulan Ini`. Percakapan dikelompokkan "
"berdasarkan operator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:115
msgid ""
":guilabel:`# of Sessions`: the number of sessions an operator participated "
"in. This measure is included by default."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`# Sesi`: jumlah sesi yang diikuti operator. Ukuran ini disertakan "
"secara default."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average duration`: the average duration of a conversation, in "
"seconds."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Durasi rata-rata`: durasi rata-rata percakapan, dalam detik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Average rating`: the average rating received by the operator."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Rating rata-rata`: rating rata-rata yang diterima oleh operator."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:119
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time to answer`: the average amount of time before the operator "
"responds to a chat request, in seconds."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Waktu untuk menjawab`: jumlah waktu rata-rata sebelum operator "
"merespons permintaan chat, dalam detik."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/reports.rst:None
msgid "Example of the Operator Analysis report from the Live Chat application."
msgstr "Contoh laporan Analisis Operator dari aplikasi Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:3
msgid "Commands and canned responses"
msgstr "Perintah dan respons cepat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the Odoo **Live Chat** application, *commands* allow the user to perform "
"specific actions both inside the chat window, and through other Odoo "
"applications. The **Live Chat** app also includes *canned responses*. These "
"are customized, preconfigured substitutions that allow users to replace "
"shortcut entries in place of longer, well-thought out responses to some of "
"the most common questions and comments."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi **Live Chat** Odoo, *perintah* memungkinkan user melakukan "
"tindakan tertentu di dalam jendela chat maupun melalui aplikasi Odoo "
"lainnya. Aplikasi **Live Chat** juga menyertakan *respons cepat*. Ini adalah "
"substitusi yang disesuaikan dan telah dikonfigurasi sebelumnya yang "
"memungkinkan user mengganti entri pintasan sebagai pengganti respons yang "
"lebih panjang dan terpikirkan dengan baik untuk beberapa pertanyaan dan "
"komentar yang paling umum."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:11
msgid ""
"Both commands and canned responses save time, and allow users to maintain a "
"level of consistency throughout their conversations."
msgstr ""
"Baik perintah maupun respons cepat menghemat waktu dan memungkinkan user "
"mempertahankan tingkat konsistensi di seluruh percakapan mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:15
msgid "Execute a command"
msgstr "Menjalankan perintah"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:17
msgid ""
"Live chat *commands* are keywords that trigger preconfigured actions. When a "
"live chat *operator* is participating in a conversation with a customer or "
"website visitor, they can execute a command by typing `/`, followed by the "
"command."
msgstr ""
"*Perintah* live chat adalah kata kunci yang memicu tindakan yang telah "
"dikonfigurasi sebelumnya. Ketika *operator* live chat berpartisipasi dalam "
"percakapan dengan pelanggan atau pengunjung website, mereka dapat "
"menjalankan perintah dengan mengetik `/`, diikuti dengan perintah tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:21
msgid ""
"Commands, and the resulting actions, are only visible in the conversation "
"window for the live chat operator. A customer does not see any commands that "
"an operator uses in a conversation from their view of the chat."
msgstr ""
"Perintah, dan tindakan yang dihasilkan, hanya terlihat di jendela percakapan "
"untuk operator live chat. Pelanggan tidak melihat perintah apa pun yang "
"digunakan operator dalam percakapan dari tampilan chat mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:26
msgid ""
"During a conversation with a customer, a live chat operator executes the "
"command to :ref:`create a ticket <live-chat/ticket>`. After entering the "
"command, `/ticket`, the system automatically creates a ticket with the "
"information from the conversation. It also includes a link to the new "
"ticket, so the operator can go there directly to add any additional "
"information, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Selama percakapan dengan pelanggan, operator live chat menjalankan perintah "
"untuk :ref:`membuat tiket <live-chat/ticket>`. Setelah memasukkan perintah `/"
"ticket`, sistem secara otomatis membuat tiket dengan informasi dari "
"percakapan. Ini juga mencakup tautan ke tiket baru, sehingga operator dapat "
"langsung ke sana untuk menambahkan informasi tambahan jika diperlukan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:34
msgid "More information about each available command can be found below."
msgstr ""
"Informasi lebih lanjut tentang setiap perintah yang tersedia dapat ditemukan "
"di bawah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:37
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Help"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:39
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/help` in the chat window, an informative message that "
"includes the potential entry types an operator can make is displayed."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator mengetik `/help` di jendela chat, pesan informatif yang "
"mencakup jenis entri potensial yang dapat dibuat operator akan ditampilkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:42
msgid ""
"Type `@username` to mention a user in the conversation. A notification will "
"be sent to that user's inbox or email, depending on their notification "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Ketik `@username` untuk menyebutkan user dalam percakapan. Notifikasi akan "
"dikirim ke inbox atau email user tersebut, tergantung pada pengaturan "
"notifikasi mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:44
msgid "Type `/command` to execute a command."
msgstr "Ketik `/command` untuk menjalankan perintah."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:45
msgid ""
"Type `:shortcut` to insert a :ref:`canned response <live-chat/canned-"
"responses>`."
msgstr ""
"Ketik `:shortcut` untuk menyisipkan :ref:`respons cepat <live-chat/canned-"
"responses>`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:48
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:49
msgid ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/productivity/discuss/team_communication`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:52
msgid "Ticket & search tickets"
msgstr "Tiket & cari tiket"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:54
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands allow operators to create "
"helpdesk tickets directly from a conversation, and search through existing "
"tickets by keyword or ticket number."
msgstr ""
"Perintah `/ticket` dan `/search_tickets` memungkinkan operator membuat tiket "
"Pusat Bantuan langsung dari percakapan, dan mencari melalui tiket yang ada "
"berdasarkan kata kunci atau nomor tiket."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:58
msgid ""
"The `/ticket` and `/search_tickets` commands can **only** be used if the "
"**Helpdesk** app has been installed, and *Live Chat* has been activated on a "
"*Helpdesk* team. To activate *Live Chat*, go to :menuselection:`Helpdesk app "
"--> Configuration --> Helpdesk Teams`, and select a team. Scroll to "
"the :guilabel:`Channels` section, and check the box labeled, :guilabel:`Live "
"Chat`."
msgstr ""
"Perintah `/ticket` dan `/search_tickets` **hanya** dapat digunakan jika "
"aplikasi **Pusat Bantuan** telah diinstal, dan *Live Chat* telah diaktifkan "
"pada tim *Pusat Bantuan*. Untuk mengaktifkan *Live Chat*, buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat Bantuan --> Konfigurasi --> Tim Pusat "
"Bantuan`, dan pilih tim. Gulir ke bagian :guilabel:`Saluran`, dan centang "
"kotak berlabel :guilabel:`Live Chat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:66
msgid "Create a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Membuat tiket dari live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:68
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/ticket` in the chat window, the conversation is used "
"to create a *Helpdesk* ticket."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator mengetik `/ticket` di jendela chat, percakapan digunakan untuk "
"membuat tiket *Pusat Bantuan*."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:71
msgid ""
"After entering the `/ticket` command, type a title for the ticket into the "
"chat window, then press `Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memasukkan perintah `/ticket`, ketik judul untuk tiket ke dalam "
"jendela chat, lalu tekan `Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a helpdesk search in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Tampilan hasil dari pencarian Pusat Bantuan dalam percakapan Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:77
msgid ""
"The newly created ticket will be added to the *Helpdesk* team that has live "
"chat enabled. If more than one team has live chat enabled, the ticket will "
"automatically be assigned based on the team's priority."
msgstr ""
"Tiket yang baru dibuat akan ditambahkan ke tim *Pusat Bantuan* yang "
"mengaktifkan live chat. Jika lebih dari satu tim mengaktifkan live chat, "
"tiket akan secara otomatis ditugaskan berdasarkan prioritas tim."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:81
msgid ""
"The transcript from the conversation will be added to the new ticket, under "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab."
msgstr ""
"Transkrip dari percakapan akan ditambahkan ke tiket baru, di bawah tab "
":guilabel:`Deskripsi`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:84
msgid ""
"To access the new ticket, click on the link in the chat window, or go to "
"the :menuselection:`Helpdesk app` and click the :guilabel:`Tickets` button "
"on the Kanban card for the appropriate team."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengakses tiket baru, klik tautan di jendela obrolan, atau buka "
":menuselection:`aplikasi Pusat Bantuan` dan klik tombol :guilabel:`Tiket` "
"pada kartu Kanban untuk tim yang sesuai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:89
msgid "Search for a ticket from a live chat"
msgstr "Mencari tiket dari live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:91
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/search_tickets` in the chat window, they can search "
"through *Helpdesk* tickets, either by ticket number or keyword."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator mengetik `/search_tickets` di jendela obrolan, mereka dapat "
"mencari melalui tiket *Pusat Bantuan*, baik berdasarkan nomor tiket atau "
"kata kunci."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:94
msgid ""
"After entering the `/search_tickets` command, type a keyword or ticket "
"number, then press :kbd:`Enter`. If one or more related tickets are found, a "
"list of links is generated in the conversation window."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memasukkan perintah `/search_tickets`, ketik kata kunci atau nomor "
"tiket, kemudian tekan :kbd:`Enter`. Jika satu atau lebih tiket terkait "
"ditemukan, daftar tautan akan dihasilkan di jendela percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:102
msgid ""
"Results from the search command will only be seen by the operator, not the "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Hasil dari perintah pencarian hanya akan dilihat oleh operator, bukan "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:105
msgid "History"
msgstr "Riwayat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:107
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/history` in the chat window, it generates a list of "
"the most recent pages the visitor has viewed on the website (up to 15)."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator mengetik `/history` di jendela obrolan, akan menghasilkan "
"daftar halaman terbaru yang telah dilihat pengunjung di website (hingga 15)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid ""
"View of the results from a /history command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Tampilan hasil dari perintah /history dalam percakapan Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:114
msgid "Lead"
msgstr "Prospek"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:116
msgid ""
"By typing `/lead` in the chat window, an operator can create a *lead* in the "
"**CRM** application."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengetik `/lead` di jendela obrolan, operator dapat membuat *prospek* "
"di aplikasi **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:None
msgid "View of the results from a /lead command in a Live Chat conversation."
msgstr "Tampilan hasil dari perintah /lead dalam percakapan Live Chat."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:122
msgid ""
"The `/lead` command can only be used if the **CRM** app has been installed."
msgstr ""
"Perintah `/lead` hanya dapat digunakan jika aplikasi **CRM** telah diinstal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:124
msgid ""
"After typing `/lead`, create a title for this new lead, then press `Enter`. "
"A link with the lead title appears. Click the link, or navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app to view the :guilabel:`Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Setelah mengetik `/lead`, buat judul untuk prospek baru ini, kemudian tekan "
"`Enter`. Tautan dengan judul prospek akan muncul. Klik tautan, atau navigasi "
"ke aplikasi :menuselection:`CRM` untuk melihat :guilabel:`Pipeline`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:129
msgid ""
"The link to the new lead can only be seen and accessed by the operator, not "
"the customer."
msgstr ""
"Tautan ke prospek baru hanya dapat dilihat dan diakses oleh operator, bukan "
"pelanggan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:131
msgid ""
"The transcript of that specific live chat conversation (where the lead was "
"created) is added to the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab of the lead form."
msgstr ""
"Transkrip dari percakapan live chat tertentu (di mana prospek dibuat) "
"ditambahkan ke tab :guilabel:`Catatan Internal` dari formulir prospek."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:134
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Extra Information` tab of the lead form, "
"the :guilabel:`Source` will be listed as :guilabel:`Livechat`."
msgstr ""
"Pada tab :guilabel:`Informasi Tambahan` dari formulir prospek, "
":guilabel:`Sumber` akan tercantum sebagai :guilabel:`Livechat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:138
msgid "Leave"
msgstr "Keluar"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:140
msgid ""
"If an operator types `/leave` in the chat window, they can automatically "
"exit the conversation. This command does not cause the customer to be "
"removed from the conversation, nor does it automatically end the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Jika operator mengetik `/leave` di jendela obrolan, mereka dapat keluar "
"secara otomatis dari percakapan. Perintah ini tidak menyebabkan pelanggan "
"dihapus dari percakapan, dan juga tidak secara otomatis mengakhiri "
"percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:145
msgid ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:146
msgid ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../services/helpdesk`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:151
msgid "Canned responses"
msgstr "Tanggapan Otomatis"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:153
msgid ""
"*Canned responses* are customizable inputs where a *shortcut* stands in for "
"a longer response. An operator will enter the shortcut, and it is "
"automatically replaced by the expanded *substitution* response in the "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"*Respons siap pakai* adalah input yang dapat disesuaikan di mana *pintasan* "
"menggantikan respons yang lebih panjang. Operator akan memasukkan pintasan, "
"dan secara otomatis diganti dengan respons *substitusi* yang diperluas dalam "
"percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:158
msgid "Create canned responses"
msgstr "Membuat respons siap pakai"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:160
msgid ""
"To create a new canned response, go to :menuselection:`Live Chat app --> "
"Configuration --> Canned Responses --> New`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat respons cepat baru, buka :menuselection:`Aplikasi Live "
"Chat --> Konfigurasi --> Respons Cepat --> Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:163
msgid ""
"Type a shortcut command in the :guilabel:`Shortcut` field. Next, click "
"the :guilabel:`Substitution` field, and type the message that should replace "
"the shortcut."
msgstr ""
"Ketik perintah pintasan di kolom :guilabel:`Pintasan`. Selanjutnya, klik "
"kolom :guilabel:`Substitusi`, dan ketik pesan yang harus menggantikan "
"pintasan tersebut."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:167
msgid ""
"Try to connect the shortcut to the topic of the substitution. The easier it "
"is for the operators to remember, the easier it is to use the canned "
"responses in conversations."
msgstr ""
"Usahakan menghubungkan pintasan dengan topik substitusi. Semakin mudah "
"operator mengingatnya, semakin mudah menggunakan respons cepat dalam "
"percakapan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:171
msgid "Authorized groups"
msgstr "Grup yang diizinkan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:173
msgid ""
"When a new canned response is created, it can **only** be utilized by the "
"operator that created it. To allow the response to be used by other "
"operators, select one or more :ref:`groups <access-rights/groups>` from "
"the :guilabel:`Authorized Groups` drop-down list."
msgstr ""
"Ketika respons cepat baru dibuat, respons tersebut **hanya** dapat digunakan "
"oleh operator yang membuatnya. Untuk mengizinkan respons tersebut digunakan "
"oleh operator lain, pilih satu atau lebih :ref:`grup <access-rights/groups>` "
"dari daftar drop-down :guilabel:`Grup yang Diizinkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:178
msgid "Use canned responses in a live chat conversation"
msgstr "Gunakan respons cepat dalam percakapan live chat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:180
msgid ""
"To use a canned response in a conversation, click the :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon in the message window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Insert a Canned Response`. This opens a list of available "
"canned responses. Either select a response from the list, or type the "
"appropriate shortcut, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-"
"plane` :guilabel:`(send)` icon or hit :kbd:`Enter`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menggunakan respons cepat dalam percakapan, klik ikon :icon:`fa-plus-"
"circle` :guilabel:`(plus)` di jendela pesan. Kemudian, klik "
":guilabel:`Sisipkan Respons Cepat`. Ini akan membuka daftar respons cepat "
"yang tersedia. Pilih respons dari daftar, atau ketik pintasan yang sesuai, "
"lalu klik ikon :icon:`fa-paper-plane` :guilabel:`(kirim)` atau tekan "
":kbd:`Enter`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:186
msgid ""
"Typing `::` into a chat window on its own generates a list of available "
"canned responses. Responses can be manually selected from the list, in "
"addition to the use of shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Mengetik `::` di jendela chat akan menghasilkan daftar respons cepat yang "
"tersedia. Respons dapat dipilih secara manual dari daftar, selain "
"menggunakan pintasan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/livechat/responses.rst:0
msgid "View of a chat window and the list of available canned responses."
msgstr "Tampilan jendela chat dan daftar respons cepat yang tersedia."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:7
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:9
msgid ""
"**Odoo Website** offers a user-friendly platform for creating and managing "
"your website. It includes various tools and features to help you design, "
"publish, and maintain web pages without needing advanced technical skills. "
"You can easily customize layouts, add multimedia content, and integrate with "
"other Odoo apps to expand your website's functionality."
msgstr ""
"**Odoo Website** menawarkan platform yang mudah digunakan untuk membuat dan "
"mengelola situs web Anda. Platform ini mencakup berbagai alat dan fitur "
"untuk membantu Anda merancang, mempublikasikan, dan memelihara halaman web "
"tanpa memerlukan keterampilan teknis tingkat lanjut. Anda dapat dengan mudah "
"menyesuaikan tata letak, menambahkan konten multimedia, dan berintegrasi "
"dengan aplikasi Odoo lainnya untuk memperluas fungsionalitas situs web Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:16
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/web_design.rst:7
msgid "Web design"
msgstr "Design website"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:16
msgid "Design your website using building blocks and website themes."
msgstr "Desain website Anda menggunakan blok bangunan dan tema website."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:22
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure.rst:7
msgid "Structure"
msgstr "Struktur"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:22
msgid "Manage website pages, menus, and search engine optimization."
msgstr "Kelola halaman website, menu, dan optimasi mesin pencari."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:28
msgid ""
"Configure domain names, address autocompletion, Google Search Console, "
"cookies bar, translations, multiple websites, form spam protection, content "
"delivery network (CDN)."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi nama domain, pelengkapan otomatis alamat, Google Search Console, "
"cookies bar, terjemahan, beberapa website, perlindungan spam formulir, "
"content delivery network (CDN)."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:35
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/reporting.rst:5
msgid "Reporting"
msgstr "Laporan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:35
msgid ""
"Monitor your website's traffic with website analytics and set up link "
"trackers."
msgstr ""
"Pantau lalu lintas website Anda dengan analitik website dan atur link "
"tracker."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:40
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/mail_groups.rst:3
msgid "Mail groups"
msgstr "Grup surat"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:40
msgid ""
"Configure mail groups to allow website visitors to participate in public "
"discussions via email."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurasi grup mail untuk memungkinkan pengunjung website berpartisipasi "
"dalam diskusi publik melalui email."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website.rst:54
msgid ":doc:`../general/integrations/unsplash`"
msgstr ":doc:`../general/integrations/unsplash`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:3
msgid "Set up a content delivery network (CDN)"
msgstr "Setup content delivery network (CDN)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:8
msgid "Deploying with KeyCDN"
msgstr "Deploying with KeyCDN"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:10
msgid ""
"A :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` or *content distribution network*, "
"is a geographically distributed network of servers that provides high speed "
"internet content. The :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` provides quick, "
"high-quality content delivery for content-heavy websites."
msgstr ""
":abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` atau *content distribution network*, "
"adalah jaringan server yang terdistribusi secara geografis yang menyediakan  "
"konten internet berkecepatan tinggi. :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` "
"menyediakan pengiriman konten yang cepat & berkualitas tinggi untuk website "
"yang penuh konten."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:14
msgid ""
"This document will guide you through the setup of a KeyCDN_ account with an "
"Odoo powered website."
msgstr ""
"Dokumen ini akan memandu Anda melalui setup akun KeyCDN_ dengan website "
"berternaga Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:17
msgid "Create a pull zone in the KeyCDN dashboard"
msgstr "Membuat pull zone di dashboard KeyCDN"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:19
msgid ""
"On the KeyCDN dashboard, start by navigating to the :menuselection:`Zones` "
"menu item on the left. On the form, give a value to the :guilabel:`Zone "
"Name`, which will appear as part of the :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery "
"Network)`'s :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`. Then, set "
"the :guilabel:`Zone Status` to :guilabel:`active` to engage the zone. For "
"the :guilabel:`Zone Type` set the value to :guilabel:`Pull`, and then, "
"finally, under the :guilabel:`Pull Settings`, enter the :guilabel:`Origin "
"URL`— this address should be the full Odoo database :abbr:`URL (Uniform "
"Resource Locator)`."
msgstr ""
"Pada dashboard KeyCDN, mulai dengan menavigasi ke menu item "
":menuselection:`Zones` di kiri. Di formulir, berikan value ke "
":guilabel:`Nama Zona`, yang akan muncul sebagai bagian dari :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)`. Lalu, "
"tetapkan :guilabel:`Status Zona` menjadi :guilabel:`aktif` untuk "
"mengaktifkan zona. Untuk :guilabel:`Tipe Zona` tetapkan value menjadi "
":guilabel:`Pull`, lalu, akhirnya, di bawah :guilabel:`Pengaturan Pull`, "
"masukkan :guilabel:`URL Asal`— alamat ini harus merupakan :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` database lengkap Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:28
msgid ""
"Use ``https://yourdatabase.odoo.com`` and replace the *yourdatabase* "
"subdomain prefix with the actual name of the database. A custom :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` can be used, as well, in place of the Odoo "
"subdomain that was provided to the database."
msgstr ""
"Gunakan ``https://databaseAnda.odoo.com`` dan ganti awalan subdomain "
"*databaseAnda* dengan nama database. :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` "
"kustom dapat juga digunakan sebagai ganti subdomain Odoo yang disediakan "
"untuk database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "KeyCDN's Zone configuration page."
msgstr "Halaman konfigurasi Zona KeyCDN."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:36
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`General Settings` heading below the zone form, click "
"the :guilabel:`Show all settings` button to expand the zone options. This "
"should be the last option on the page. After expanding "
"the :guilabel:`General Settings` ensure that the :guilabel:`CORS` option "
"is :guilabel:`enabled`."
msgstr ""
"Di bawah heading :guilabel:`Pengaturan Umum` di bawah formulir zona, klik "
"tombol :guilabel:`Tunjukkan semua pengaturan` untuk membuka opsi zona. Ini "
"harusnya merupakan opsi terakhir di halaman. Setelah membuka "
":guilabel:`Pengaturan Umum` pastikan bahwa opsi :guilabel:`CORS` "
":guilabel:`diaktifkan`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:41
msgid ""
"Next, scroll to the bottom of the zone configuration page "
"and :guilabel:`Save` the changes. KeyCDN will indicate that the new zone "
"will be deployed. This can take about 10 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Lalu, scroll ke bagian bawah halaman konfigurasi zona dan :guilabel:`Simpan` "
"perubahan. KeyCDN akan mengindikasikan bahwa zona baru akan di-deploy. Ini "
"dapat memakan waktu sampai 10 menit."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "KeyCDN deploying the new Zone."
msgstr "KeyCDN mendeploy Zona baru."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:49
msgid ""
"A new :guilabel:`Zone URL` has been generated for your Zone, in this example "
"it is ``pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com``. This value will differ for each database."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL Zona` baru telah dibuat untuk Zona Anda, pada contoh ini "
"adalah ``pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com``. Value ini akan berbeda untuk setiap "
"database."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:52
msgid ""
"Copy this :guilabel:`Zone URL` to a text editor for later, as it will be "
"used in the next steps."
msgstr ""
"Salin :guilabel:`URL Zona` ini ke text editor untuk nanti, karena akan "
"digunakan di langkah-langkah berikutnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:55
msgid "Configure the Odoo instance with the new zone"
msgstr "Konfigurasikan instansi Odoo dengan zona baru"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:57
msgid ""
"In the Odoo :guilabel:`Website` app, go to the :menuselection:`Settings` and "
"then activate the :guilabel:`Content Delivery Network (CDN)` setting and "
"copy/paste the :guilabel:`Zone URL` value from the earlier step into "
"the :guilabel:`CDN Base URL` field. This field is only visible and "
"configurable when the :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is activated."
msgstr ""
"Di aplikasi :guilabel:`Website` Odoo, buka :menuselection:`Pengaturan` "
"kemudian aktifkan pengaturan :guilabel:`Content Delivery Network (CDN)` dan "
"salin/tempel nilai :guilabel:`URL Zona` dari langkah sebelumnya ke dalam "
"kolom :guilabel:`URL Dasar CDN`. Kolom ini hanya terlihat dan dapat "
"dikonfigurasi ketika :ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>` diaktifkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:63
msgid ""
"Ensure that there are two *forward slashes* (`//`) before the :guilabel:`CDN "
"Base URL` and one forward slash (`/`) after the :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`."
msgstr ""
"Pastikan terdapat dua *garis miring* (`//`) sebelum :guilabel:`CDN Base URL` "
"dan satu garis miring (`/`) setelah :guilabel:`CDN Base URL`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`Save` the settings when complete."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Simpan` pengaturan saat selesai."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "Activate the CDN setting in Odoo."
msgstr "Aktifkan pengaturan CDN di Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:72
msgid ""
"Now the website is using the CDN for the resources matching "
"the :guilabel:`CDN filters` regular expressions."
msgstr ""
"Sekarang website menggunakan CDN untuk resource yang cocok dengan regular "
"expression :guilabel:`filter CDN`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:75
msgid ""
"In the HTML of the Odoo website, the :abbr:`CDN (content delivery network)` "
"integration is evidenced as working properly by checking the :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locators)` of images. The *CDN Base URL* value can be seen "
"by using your web browser's :guilabel:`Inspect` feature on the Odoo website. "
"Look for it's record by searching within the :guilabel:`Network` tab inside "
"of devtools."
msgstr ""
"Di HTML website Odoo, integrasi :abbr:`CDN (content delivery network)` "
"terbukti bekerja dengan benar dengan mengecek :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource "
"Locators)` gambar. Value *CDN Base URL* dapat dilihat dengan menggunakan "
"fitur :guilabel:`Inspect` di browser website Anda pada website Odoo. Cari "
"recordnya dengan mencari di tab :guilabel:`Network` di dalam devtools."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid ""
"The CDN Base URL can be seen using the inspect function on the Odoo website."
msgstr "CDN Base URL dapat dilihat menggunakan fungsi inspek pada website Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:85
msgid ""
"Prevent security issues by activating cross-origin resource sharing (CORS)"
msgstr ""
"Cegah masalah keamanan dengan mengaktifkan cross-origin resource sharing "
"(CORS)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:87
msgid ""
"A security restriction in some browsers (such as Mozilla Firefox and Google "
"Chrome) prevents a remotely linked CSS file to fetch relative resources on "
"this same external server."
msgstr ""
"Batasan keamanan di beberapa browser (seperti Mozillla Firefox dan Google "
"Chrome) mencegah file CSS yang secara remote di-link untuk mengambil "
"relative resource pada server eksternal yang sama ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:90
msgid ""
"If the :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` option isn't enabled in "
"the :guilabel:`CDN Zone`, the more obvious resulting problem on a standard "
"Odoo website will be the lack of *Font Awesome* icons because the font file "
"declared in the *Font Awesome* CSS won't be loaded from the remote server."
msgstr ""
"Bila opsi :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` tidak diaktifkan di "
":guilabel:`Zona CDN`, hasil masalah yang paling gampang terlihat pada "
"website standar Odoo adalah hilangnya ikon *Font Awesome* karena file font "
"yang dideklarasikan di CSS *Font Awesome* tidak akan dimuat dari server "
"remote."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:95
msgid ""
"When these cross-origin resource issues occur, a security error message "
"similar to the output below will appear in the web browser's developer "
"console:"
msgstr ""
"Saat masalah cross-origin resource ini muncul, pesan error keamanan yang "
"mirip dengan output di bawah akan muncul di developer console browser "
"website:"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:98
msgid ""
"``Font from origin 'http://pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com' has been blocked from "
"loading /shop:1 by Cross-Origin Resource Sharing policy: No 'Access-Control-"
"Allow-Origin' header is present on the requested resource. Origin 'http://"
"yourdatabase.odoo.com' is therefore not allowed access.``"
msgstr ""
"``Font dari asal 'http://pulltest-xxxxx.kxcdn.com' telah diblokir dari "
"memuat /shop:1 oleh kebijakan Cross-Origin Resource Sharing: Tidak ada "
"header 'Access-Control-Allow-Origin' di resource yang diminta. Asal URL "
"'http://databaseAnda.odoo.com' oleh karena itu tidak diizinkan mengakses.``"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:None
msgid "Error message populated in the browser console."
msgstr "Pesan error yang muncul di console browser."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cdn.rst:106
msgid ""
"Enabling the :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` option in "
"the :abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` settings fixes this issue."
msgstr ""
"Mengaktifkan opsi :abbr:`CORS (Cross-Origin Resource Sharing)` di pengaturan "
":abbr:`CDN (Content Delivery Network)` akan membetulkan masalah ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:3
msgid "Cookies bar"
msgstr "Bilah cookies"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Cookies** are small text files sent to your device when you visit a "
"website. They are processed and stored by your browser and record visitor "
"information like login details, preferences, and browsing history. "
"**Essential cookies** are necessary for the website to function, while "
"**optional cookies** are used to analyze behavior or display ads."
msgstr ""
"**Cookie** adalah file teks kecil yang dikirim ke perangkat Anda saat "
"mengunjungi website. Cookie diproses dan disimpan oleh browser Anda dan "
"merekam informasi pengunjung seperti detail login, preferensi, dan riwayat "
"penjelajahan. **Cookie esensial** diperlukan agar website berfungsi, "
"sedangkan **cookie opsional** digunakan untuk menganalisis perilaku atau "
"menampilkan iklan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:10
msgid ""
"Data protection laws require notifying visitors about data collection "
"methods and purposes. **Cookies bar** fulfill this obligation by informing "
"visitors on their first visit and allowing them to decide whether to store "
"all or only essential cookies on their device."
msgstr ""
"Undang-undang perlindungan data mengharuskan pemberitahuan kepada pengunjung "
"tentang metode dan tujuan pengumpulan data. **Bar cookie** memenuhi "
"kewajiban ini dengan memberi tahu pengunjung pada kunjungan pertama mereka "
"dan memungkinkan mereka memutuskan apakah akan menyimpan semua cookie atau "
"hanya cookie esensial di perangkat mereka."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:15
msgid ""
"Cookies bars are required to obtain visitors' consent for optional cookies "
"only. Consent is not required for essential cookies."
msgstr ""
"Bar cookie diperlukan untuk mendapatkan persetujuan pengunjung hanya untuk "
"cookie opsional. Persetujuan tidak diperlukan untuk cookie esensial."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:18
msgid ""
"Odoo is compliant with `Google consent mode v2 <https://support.google.com/"
"tagmanager/answer/13695607>`_."
msgstr ""
"Odoo mematuhi `Google consent mode v2 <https://support.google.com/tagmanager/"
"answer/13695607>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:23
msgid ""
"To add a cookies bar on your website, go to :menuselection:`Website --> "
"Configuration --> Settings` and enable :guilabel:`Cookies Bar` in "
"the :guilabel:`Tracking & SEO` section. This activates :guilabel:`Block "
"tracking 3rd-party services` by default, including social media, video "
"hosting platforms, and Google services. Click :guilabel:`Add domains to the "
"block list` to include other external websites. These services remain "
"blocked on your website until visitors accept optional cookies."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menambahkan bar cookie di website Anda, buka "
":menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` dan aktifkan "
":guilabel:`Cookies Bar` di bagian :guilabel:`Tracking & SEO`. Ini "
"mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Block tracking 3rd-party services` secara default, "
"termasuk media sosial, platform hosting video, dan layanan Google. Klik "
":guilabel:`Add domains to the block list` untuk menyertakan website "
"eksternal lainnya. Layanan ini tetap diblokir di website Anda sampai "
"pengunjung menerima cookie opsional."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:31
msgid ""
"Using third-party cookies without a cookies bar does not prevent them from "
"being triggered. Only the presence of a cookie bar **and** the visitor’s "
"refusal ensure that these cookies are blocked."
msgstr ""
"Menggunakan cookie pihak ketiga tanpa bar cookie tidak mencegah cookie "
"tersebut dipicu. Hanya keberadaan bar cookie **dan** penolakan pengunjung "
"yang memastikan bahwa cookie ini diblokir."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:37
msgid "Cookies policy"
msgstr "Kebijakan cookies"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:39
msgid ""
"When you enable the cookies bar for your website, Odoo creates the **Cookie "
"Policy** page (`/cookie-policy`) containing a list of cookies set by "
"default, with their purpose and examples."
msgstr ""
"Ketika Anda mengaktifkan bar cookie untuk website Anda, Odoo membuat halaman "
"**Cookie Policy** (`/cookie-policy`) yang berisi daftar cookie yang "
"ditetapkan secara default, beserta tujuan dan contohnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:48
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Kategori"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:49
msgid "Role"
msgstr "Peran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:50
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nama"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:51
msgid "Essential - Session & Security"
msgstr "Esensial - Sesi & Keamanan"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:52
msgid ""
"Authenticate visitors, protect visitor data and allow the website to deliver "
"the services visitors expects, such as maintaining the content of their "
"cart, or allowing file uploads. The website will not work properly without "
"these cookies."
msgstr ""
"Mengautentikasi pengunjung, melindungi data pengunjung, dan memungkinkan "
"website menyediakan layanan yang diharapkan pengunjung, seperti "
"mempertahankan konten keranjang mereka, atau memungkinkan pengunggahan file. "
"Website tidak akan berfungsi dengan baik tanpa cookie ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:55
msgid "session_id (Odoo)"
msgstr "session_id (Odoo)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:56
msgid "Essential - Preferences"
msgstr "Esensial - Preferensi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:57
msgid ""
"Remember information about the preferred look or behavior of the website, "
"such as the preferred language or region. The website will continue to "
"function without these cookies, but the visitor’s experience may be affected."
msgstr ""
"Mengingat informasi tentang tampilan atau perilaku website yang disukai, "
"seperti bahasa atau wilayah yang disukai. Website akan terus berfungsi tanpa "
"cookie ini, tetapi pengalaman pengunjung mungkin terpengaruh."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:60
msgid "frontend_lang (Odoo)"
msgstr "frontend_lang (Odoo)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:61
msgid "Optional - Interaction History"
msgstr "Opsional - Riwayat Interaksi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:62
msgid ""
"Collect information about your interactions with the website, the pages "
"you've seen, and any specific marketing campaign that brought you to the "
"website. The website will work without these cookies, but some features or "
"services may not perform optimally."
msgstr ""
"Mengumpulkan informasi tentang interaksi Anda dengan website, halaman yang "
"telah Anda lihat, dan kampanye pemasaran tertentu yang membawa Anda ke "
"website. Website akan berfungsi tanpa cookie ini, tetapi beberapa fitur atau "
"layanan mungkin tidak berkinerja optimal."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:65
msgid ""
"im_livechat_previous_operator (Odoo), utm_campaign (Odoo), utm_source "
"(Odoo), utm_medium (Odoo)"
msgstr ""
"im_livechat_previous_operator (Odoo), utm_campaign (Odoo), utm_source (Odoo)"
", utm_medium (Odoo)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:69
msgid "Optional - Advertising & Marketing"
msgstr "Opsional - Periklanan & Pemasaran"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:70
msgid ""
"Make advertising more engaging to visitors and more valuable to publishers "
"and advertisers, such as providing more relevant ads when you visit other "
"websites that display ads or to improve reporting on ad campaign "
"performance. Note that some third-party services may install additional "
"cookies on your browser in order to identify you."
msgstr ""
"Membuat iklan lebih menarik bagi pengunjung dan lebih berharga bagi penerbit "
"dan pengiklan, seperti menyediakan iklan yang lebih relevan saat Anda "
"mengunjungi website lain yang menampilkan iklan atau untuk meningkatkan "
"pelaporan kinerja kampanye iklan. Perhatikan bahwa beberapa layanan pihak "
"ketiga mungkin menginstal cookie tambahan di browser Anda untuk "
"mengidentifikasi Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:74
msgid "__gads (Google), __gac (Google)"
msgstr "__gads (Google), __gac (Google)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:76
msgid "Optional - Analytics"
msgstr "Opsional - Analitik"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:77
msgid ""
"Understand how visitors engage with the website, via Google Analytics. The "
"website will still work without these cookies."
msgstr ""
"Memahami bagaimana pengunjung berinteraksi dengan website, melalui Google "
"Analytics. Website akan tetap berfungsi tanpa cookies ini."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:79
msgid "_ga (Google), _gat (Google), _gid (Google), _gac_* (Google)"
msgstr "_ga (Google), _gat (Google), _gid (Google), _gac_* (Google)"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:85
msgid ""
"It is not possible to let visitors customize or select which optional "
"cookies they want to allow."
msgstr ""
"Tidak dimungkinkan untuk membiarkan pengunjung menyesuaikan atau memilih "
"cookies opsional mana yang ingin mereka izinkan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:88
msgid ""
"You could add a link to this page in your website's footer, for example."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menambahkan tautan ke halaman ini di footer situs web Anda, "
"misalnya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:93
msgid "Edit the Cookies policy page"
msgstr "Edit halaman kebijakan Cookies"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:95
msgid ""
"To access it, click the :guilabel:`Cookie Policy` hyperlink in the cookies "
"bar or open the page from :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengaksesnya, klik hyperlink :guilabel:`Cookie Policy` di bilah "
"cookies atau buka halaman dari :menuselection:`Website --> Site --> Pages`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:98
msgid ""
"To adapt the content of the page according to your needs, click "
"the :guilabel:`Edit` button."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan konten halaman sesuai kebutuhan Anda, klik tombol "
":guilabel:`Edit`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:101
msgid ""
"You have to list every cookie you added yourself on the `/cookie-policy` "
"page including their name, role, category and duration."
msgstr ""
"Anda harus mencantumkan setiap cookie yang Anda tambahkan sendiri di halaman "
"`/cookie-policy` termasuk nama, peran, kategori, dan durasinya."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:105
msgid "To check the duration of cookies, use your browser’s developer tools."
msgstr "Untuk memeriksa durasi cookies, gunakan developer tools browser Anda."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:108
msgid ":doc:`Pages <../structure/pages>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Halaman <../structure/pages>`"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:113
msgid "Customization"
msgstr "Kustomisasi"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:115
msgid ""
"To adapt the display of the cookies bar on your website, "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` on the website editor, go to the :guilabel:`Invisible "
"Elements` section at the bottom of the panel, and click :guilabel:`Cookies "
"Bar`. You can modify the :guilabel:`Layout` and :guilabel:`Size` of the "
"cookies bar, and enable :guilabel:`Backdrop` to gray out the page in the "
"background when the cookies bar is displayed on the screen."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menyesuaikan tampilan bilah cookies di website Anda, klik "
":guilabel:`Edit` di editor website, buka bagian :guilabel:`Invisible "
"Elements` di bagian bawah panel, dan klik :guilabel:`Cookies Bar`. Anda "
"dapat mengubah :guilabel:`Layout` dan :guilabel:`Size` bilah cookies, serta "
"mengaktifkan :guilabel:`Backdrop` untuk membuat halaman latar belakang "
"menjadi abu-abu ketika bilah cookies ditampilkan di layar."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:121
msgid ""
"Click anywhere in the building block to further customize the appearance of "
"the cookies bar using :guilabel:`Block`, :guilabel:`Column` and/"
"or :guilabel:`Inline Text` customization options."
msgstr ""
"Klik di mana saja dalam blok bangunan untuk lebih menyesuaikan tampilan "
"bilah cookies menggunakan opsi kustomisasi :guilabel:`Blok`, "
":guilabel:`Kolom` dan/atau :guilabel:`Teks Inline`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/cookies_bar.rst:124
msgid ""
"To edit the contents of the cookies bar (i.e., the consent message), click "
"directly in the building block."
msgstr ""
"Untuk mengedit konten bilah cookies (yaitu, pesan persetujuan), klik "
"langsung di blok bangunan."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:3
