msgstr "Penawaran terbatas pada pendaftaran **nama domain baru**."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/domain_names.rst:53
msgid ""
"The offer is available to *One App Free* plans. Ensure your website contains "
"sufficient original content for Odoo to verify that your request is "
"legitimate and in compliance with `Odoo's Acceptable Use Policy <https://"
"www.odoo.com/acceptable-use>`_. Given the high number of requests, it can "
"take Odoo several days to review them."
msgstr ""
"Penawaran tersedia untuk paket *One App Free*. Pastikan website Anda berisi "
"konten asli yang cukup agar Odoo dapat memverifikasi bahwa permintaan Anda "
"sah dan sesuai dengan `Kebijakan Penggunaan yang Dapat Diterima Odoo "
"<https://www.odoo.com/acceptable-use>`_. Mengingat banyaknya permintaan, "
"Odoo dapat membutuhkan beberapa hari untuk meninjaunya."

