msgstr ":guilabel:`Salin` tag HTML ke clipboard."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/google_search_console.rst:113
msgid ""
"On your Odoo website, click :guilabel:`Edit` in the upper-right corner, go "
"to the :guilabel:`Theme` tab, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Advanced` "
"section, then click :guilabel:`<head> and </body>` next to :guilabel:`Code "
