msgid ""
"Going to :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` and "
"clicking :guilabel:`+ New Website`."
msgstr ""
"Buka :menuselection:`Website --> Configuration --> Settings` dan klik "
":guilabel:`+ Website Baru`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:33
msgid ""
"Choosing a :guilabel:`Website Name` and entering the second website's "
"address in the :guilabel:`Website Domain` field (e.g., `https://"
"www.yourseconddomain.com` or `https://subdomain.yourdomain.com`)."
msgstr ""
"Pilih :guilabel:`Nama Website` dan masukkan alamat website kedua di kolom "
":guilabel:`Domain Website` (misalnya, `https://www.yourseconddomain.com` "
