#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:36
msgid "Clicking the :guilabel:`Create` button."
msgstr "Klik tombol :guilabel:`Buat`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:39
msgid ""
"To switch from one website's frontend to another, click the website "
"selection drop-down in the top right corner and select the website you want "
"to switch to."
msgstr ""
"Untuk beralih dari frontend satu website ke website lain, klik menu dropdown "
"pemilihan website di pojok kanan atas dan pilih website yang ingin Anda tuju."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/multi_website.rst:0
