":ref:`mode pengembang <developer-mode>` dan buka :menuselection:`General "
"Settings --> Technical --> System Parameters`. Klik :guilabel:`New` dan isi "
"kolom :guilabel:`Key` dan :guilabel:`Value` berikut:"

